INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(23, '首页->不忘初心->红色岁月->人->周恩来', 'Home Page->Past->Red years->people->Zhou Enlai', '1532507021', '2018-08-28', '23:59:11', '1', '<p style="text-align:center"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180814/1534220483245259.jpg" title="1534220483245259.jpg" alt="周恩来3.jpg"/></span></p><p>周恩来是声震中外的政治家、外交家。在他十二岁小的时候，就已经响亮地发出了“为中华之崛起而读书”的时代强音，周恩来同志50多年的革命生涯，同中国共产党的建立、发展、壮大，同我国新民主主义革命的胜利，同我国社会主义革命和建设的历史进程紧密联系在一起。他毫无保留地把全部精力奉献给了党和人民，直到生命的最后一息。他身上集中体现了中国共产党人的高风亮节，在中国人民心中矗立起一座不朽的丰碑。我们缅怀周恩来同志，就是要永远铭记和认真学习周恩来同志的精神，使之不断发扬光大。直到生命垂危的弥留之际，还牵挂着党和国家的前途命运。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p style="text-align:center"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180814/1534220483245259.jpg" title=" 1534220483245259.jpg" alt=" Zhou Enlai 3.jpg"/></span></p><p> Zhou Enlai is a sound foreign statesman and diplomat. When he was twelve years old and small, have been loud, &#34;the rise of the Chinese reading&#34; era forte, comrade Zhou Enlai 50 years of revolutionary career, with the Communist Party of Chinese establishment, development and growth, with China&#39;s victory in the new democratic revolution, together with the historical process of socialism in China revolution and construction. He unreservedly devoted all his energy to the party and the people, until my last breath. He epitomizes the Chinese Communists erected a exemplary conduct and nobility of character, immortal monument in the hearts of the people Chinese. We cherish the memory of Comrade Zhou Enlai, is to always remember and seriously study the spirit of Comrade Zhou Enlai, to continue to carry forward. Until dying deathbed, but also cared about the fate of the party and the state.</p><p><br/></p>', 535, 60, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(24, '首页->不忘初心->红色岁月->人->“羊书记”姜仕坤', 'Home Page->Past->Red years->people->&#34;Sheep&#34; Secretary Jiang Shikun', '1532507100', '2018-08-29', '00:03:26', '1', '<p><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180814/1534220581874622.jpg" title="1534220581874622.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;">深入边远贫困乡村察民情、解民忧,与群众算发展增收账,为群众找发展出路,是姜仕坤多年的工作常态。由于对农村工作熟悉,姜仕坤基本成为解决群众问题的活字典,干部们遇到解决不了的事情,他耐心细致教方法,并尽量抽出时间现场办公。在他的心中,根植着深厚的农民情结。他经常对农业龙头企业和金融部门说:“要把利益让给老百姓,只有老百姓发展起来了,大家才有发展。”他有一个朴素理念:“没有贫困群众的小康,就没有晴隆县的全面小康。”他获得了“羊书记”、“农民书记”、“算账书记”等群众口碑。姜仕坤走了,这位苗族汉子在生命光芒激情绽放的时候,匆匆告别他的同事、亲人和朋友,告别他深深热爱的晴隆山水、父老乡亲。他用共产党人的理想信念、忠诚无私、执著追求,用对党的赤子之心、对人民的公仆情怀,践行着时代的使命和担当,在贵州高原上谱写了感人肺腑、催人泪下的生命壮歌。<br/></p><p><br/></p>', '<p><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180814/1534220581874622.jpg" title=" 1534220581874622.jpg"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;"> Go to remote rural poverty to observe the people, the people to worry, and the masses is increase the development of accounts receivable, find way out for the masses, ginger is Shikun years of work norm. The familiar with the rural work, Jiang Shikun became the basic living dictionary solves the problems of the masses, cadres have encountered solve things, he patiently teaching method, and try to find time to site office. In his heart, a deep rooted farmer complex. He is often the leading agricultural enterprises and the financial sector said: &#34;to the benefit to the people, only people developed, we have development.&#34; He has a simple concept: &#34;there is no poor people off, no Qinglong County Comprehensive well-off.&#34; He won the &#34;sheep&#34; farmer secretary, secretary, Secretary of afterwards &#34;the reputation of the masses. Jiang Shikun is gone, when the man in the light of Miao life passion, hurried goodbye to his colleagues, relatives and friends, say goodbye to his beloved Qinglong landscape, folks. He used the ideal faith, loyalty, selfless Communist pursuit, with the party and the people&#39;s public servant feelings utter innocence, embody the mission of the times and play, write a copy from rolia, touch one deeply in the heart ZhuangGe life in Guizhou plateau.<br/></p><p><br/></p>', 554, 100, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(25, '首页->不忘初心->红色岁月->人->木拉提·西日甫江', 'Home Page->Past->Red years->people->Mulati Sizhivko', '1532507181', '2018-08-29', '00:03:43', '1', '<p style="text-align:center"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180814/1534220656262037.jpg" title="1534220656262037.jpg" alt="木拉提3.jpg"/></p><p>和田是暴力恐怖斗争的前沿阵地，面对艰巨繁重和复杂危险的维稳任务，木拉提·西日甫江与犯罪分子机智周旋、斗智斗勇，先后数十次将暴恐犯罪活动粉碎在预谋之中，他也因此被当地群众誉为“猎鹰”(维吾尔语的尊称，传说中老百姓的守护者)。钢的意志，铁的臂膀，每天都在与死亡的狂沙较量。危险无处不在，他用胸膛作盾牌;为了同胞的安宁，他选择了翱翔。高飞的猎鹰，他绝不孤独，因为身后是人民!他是新疆和田地区公安局民警木拉提•西日甫江，数十次将暴恐犯罪活动打击在预谋之中。</p>', '<p style="text-align:center"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180814/1534220656262037.jpg" title=" 1534220656262037.jpg" alt=" Mulati 3.jpg"/></p><p> Hotan is the frontier of violent terrorist struggle, facing the arduous task of maintaining stability and complex risk, deal with criminals, Mulati Si Rifu Jiang wit wits for dozens of times, the fear of violence and criminal activities in crushing premeditated, and thus he was the local people as the &#34;Falcon&#34; (honorific, Uyghur language the legendary people&#39;s guardian). Steel will, iron arms, in the sand and death contest every day. The risk is everywhere, he used as a shield to fellow chest; peace, he chose to fly. Goofy falcon, he is never lonely, because behind people! He is in Hetian area of Xinjiang Public Security Bureau police Mulati Rifu West River, dozens of violent terrorist crimes will blow in premeditated.</p>', 296, 54, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(26, '首页->不忘初心->红色岁月->路->长征路', 'Home Page->Past->Red years->road->Long road', '1532508005', '2018-08-26', '08:16:15', '1', '<p style=";background:white"><strong><span style="font-size:29px;font-family:宋体;color:red"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180814/1534220711656647.jpg" title="1534220711656647.jpg" alt="长征路3.jpg" width="892" height="362"/></span></strong></p><p>长征路：长征精神，是中华民族百折不挠、自强不息的民族精神的最高体现，是保证中国革命和建设事业从胜利走向胜利的强大精神力量。真正属于历史的同样属于未来。80年光阴荏苒，长征精神作为中华民族精神宝库的重要组成部分，今天仍然焕发着不朽的生命力，始终是激励我们顽强奋斗、勇往直前的强大动力和宝贵财富。只有铭记历史，才能深刻了解过去，全面把握现在，正确创造未来。纪念红军长征胜利80周年，最重要的就是要缅怀革命先辈的不朽功勋，继承光荣革命传统，发扬伟大长征精神，同心同德、艰苦奋斗，在建设富强民主文明和谐的社会主义现代化国家、实现中华民族伟大复兴的新长征道路上不断创造新的业绩。<span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 宋体"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180725/1532507983488895.jpg" title="1532507983488895.jpg" alt="长征.jpg" width="953" height="393"/></span></p><p>弘扬长征精神，重走长征路：</p><p>（1）广西来宾国税干部：深入基层送政策送服务 走好新的长征路</p><p>“弘扬伟大长征精神，走好今天的长征路。总书记的这句话，是为了激励我们不忘初心，铭记长征故事，将长征过程中红军所坚持的精神发挥在我们工作领域中，即使是在平凡的岗位上也能创造出人生价值。” 广西来宾市国地税合作办公室干部吴卜升说。</p><p>（2）北京西城区百名党员什刹海畔重走“长征路”</p><p>纪念活动以“学习党章 重温誓词 走长征路”为主题，重温入党誓词之后，百余名党员模拟红军长征路线围绕前海健走一周，沿途参观《寻访长征足迹 传承长征精神》展览。展览以前海小广场为主场地，沿途设立3个分站，分别代表瑞金、遵义和会宁。每到一处，党员、职工都认真地驻足观看。金沙江的激流、泸定桥的战火、雪山的严寒和草地的凶险衬托出红军指战员的勇气与信念，激发着参观者对理想与事业的追求与忠诚，从而达到以党的历史教育党员，以榜样的力量引领党员的宣传效果。</p><p>（3）“健康中国 重走长征路”广西站在兴安县启动</p><p>“健康中国——重走长征路，关注支持基层医疗，致中华医学会百年庆典活动”广西站活动，在桂林市兴安县红军长征突破湘江烈士纪念碑园前启动。“健康中国——重走长征路”广西站活动为期两天，活动包括启动仪式、诊疗产品展示车观摩、县级医院院长论坛及医师培训观摩等，近２００名来自广西各地市县级医院的医师参加了培训。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p style=";background:white"><strong><span style="font-size:29px;font-family:宋体;color:red"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180814/1534220711656647.jpg" title=" 1534220711656647.jpg" alt=" Long road 3.jpg" width="892" height="362"/></span></strong></p><p> The long march: the long march spirit, is the highest expression of the Chinese people&#39;s national spirit of unremitting self-improvement, never yield in spite of reverses, is to ensure the Chinese revolution and construction from victory to the powerful spirit. Really belongs to history but also belongs to the future. 80 years Time passes very quickly. as an important part of the long march spirit, spiritual treasure of the Chinese nation, today is still shining vitality, is always a powerful driving force and precious wealth of tenacious struggle and courage to inspire us. Only remember history, to understand the past, grasp right now, create the future. To commemorate the victory of the Red Army in 80th anniversary, the most important is to cherish the memory of immortal feats of revolutionary predecessors, inherit the glorious revolutionary tradition, carry forward the great spirit of the Long March, of one heart and one mind and hard work, and constantly create new achievements in building a prosperous, democratic and civilized and harmonious modern socialist country and achieve the great rejuvenation of the new long march on the road.<span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 宋体"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180725/1532507983488895.jpg" title=" 1532507983488895.jpg" alt=" The long march.Jpg" width="953" height="393"/></span></p><p> Carry forward the spirit of the Long March, long march:</p><p> (1) Guangxi: grassroots cadres guest tax policy to send delivery service along the new long march road</p><p> &#34;Carry forward the great spirit of the Long March, along today&#39;s long road. This sentence is the general secretary, to motivate us to forget the beginning of the heart, bearing in mind the long story, the long march of the Red Army in the process of adhere to the spirit of play in our work in the field, it can create the value of life in the ordinary post.&#34; Guangxi Laibin City State Tax Cooperation Office cadres Wu Busheng said.</p><p> (2) Beijing Xicheng District 100 members of Shichahai side go the long way&#34;</p><p> In commemoration of &#34;learning party constitution relive the oath Long March&#34; as the theme, then review the party oath, hundreds of members of simulated Red Army lines around Qianhai walking along the way to visit &#34;for a week, the long march spirit&#34; footprint heritage exhibition. The exhibition in Qianhai Plaza site, along the way to set up 3 sub stations, representing Ruijin, Zunyi and huining. In every place, Party members and workers carefully watch. Jinsha river rapids, bridge the war, snow cold and grass off the dangerous Red Army officers and men of courage and faith, to inspire visitors to the ideal and pursuit of the cause and loyalty, so as to achieve the party history education of Party members, Party members and leading to an example of the power of advertising effect.</p><p> (3) &#34;health China Long March&#34; Guangxi station launched in Xingan County</p><p> &#34;Health China - Long March, pay attention to support primary care, by the Chinese Medical Association Centennial activities Guangxi station activities, in the Xingan County of Guilin City long breakthrough Xiangjiang Martyrs Memorial Park before the start. &#34;Health Chinese - Long March&#34; Guangxi station activities for a period of two days, the activities include the launching ceremony, medical products show car, county-level hospital forum and physician training observation, nearly 200 people from around the city of Guangxi county hospital physicians participated in the training.</p><p><br/></p>', 439, 60, '');
