INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(31, '首页->不忘初心->红色岁月->精神->长征精神', 'Home Page->Past->Red years->spirit->the spirit of the long march', '1532508357', '2018-08-29', '00:04:09', '1', '<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;">长征精神</p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;">（1）时代背景</p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180725/1532508325306474.jpg" title="1532508325306474.jpg" alt="毛浙东.jpg"/></p><p>    长征精神是中国共产党在二万五千里长征中创造的革命精神。1934年至1935年中国工农红军经历的二万五千里长征是人类战争史上的奇迹。红军指战员在长征途中表现出对革命理想和事业无比的忠诚、坚定的信念，表现出不怕牺牲、敢于胜利的无产阶级革命乐观主义精神，表现出顾全大局、严守纪律、亲密团结的高尚品德，创造了伟大的长征精神。集中体现为：坚忍不拔，自强不息，勇往直前。最显著特点是“一不怕苦，二不怕死”的革命英雄主义精神。长征精神是中华民族百折不挠、自强不息的民族精神的最高表现，是保证我们革命和建设事业从胜利走向胜利的强大精神力量。</p><p> 1934年10月，第五次反“围剿”战争失败后，中央红军主力被迫撤离江西革命根据地，准备与二、六军团会合，沿途突破敌人四道封锁线，兵力损失五万余人。12月，<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%BB%8E%E5%B9%B3%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%AE" target="_blank">黎平会议</a>召开后，红军改变会合计划，向贵州腹地进发。1935年1月，红军攻打<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%A8%84%E5%B1%B1%E5%85%B3" target="_blank">娄山关</a>，占领遵义城，召开政治局扩大</p><p>会议，毛泽东在中央的领导地位也开始确立。会后，红军四渡赤水河、<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%B7%A7%E6%B8%A1%E9%87%91%E6%B2%99%E6%B1%9F" target="_blank">巧渡金沙江</a>、<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%BC%BA%E6%B8%A1%E5%A4%A7%E6%B8%A1%E6%B2%B3" target="_blank">强渡大渡河</a>、翻越夹金山。6月，与红四方面军会合，开始与张国焘的分裂主义作斗争，左路军走过人迹罕至的草地。随后，红一，三军团和军委纵队继续北上，攻克天险腊子口，翻越<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%85%AD%E7%9B%98%E5%B1%B1" target="_blank">六盘山</a>，到达吴起镇与<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%99%95%E5%8C%97%E7%BA%A2%E5%86%9B" target="_blank">陕北红军</a>会师，中央红军长征宣告结束。1936年10月中国工农红军第一、二、四方面军在甘肃省会宁地区会师，红军宣布长征胜利结</p><p>(2)定义</p><p>乐于吃苦，不惧<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%89%B0%E9%9A%BE%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD" target="_blank">艰难的革命</a>乐观主义；勇于战斗，<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%97%A0%E5%9D%9A%E4%B8%8D%E6%91%A7" target="_blank">无坚不摧</a>的革命英雄主义；重于求实，独立自主的创新胆略；善于团结，顾全大局的集体主义。其主题是“一不怕苦，二不怕死”；其最显著的特点就是革命英雄主义精神。长征精神是中华民族百折不挠、<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%87%AA%E5%BC%BA%E4%B8%8D%E6%81%AF" target="_blank">自强不息</a>的民族精神的最高表现，是保证我们革命和建设事业从弱小走向强大的精神力量。</p><p><a></a><a></a><a></a> </p><p>什么是长征精神？</p><p>   <a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%95%BF%E5%BE%81/22312" target="_blank">长征</a>是中华民族不屈不挠精神的典范。纵观整个长征的过程：四渡赤水河，巧渡<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%87%91%E6%B2%99%E6%B1%9F" target="_blank">金沙江</a>；飞夺<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%B3%B8%E5%AE%9A%E6%A1%A5" target="_blank">泸定桥</a>，强渡大渡河，爬雪山，过草地……每一个战略方向的改变，每一项战略任务的确定，每一次战斗胜利的取得，都无不体现出中国红军将士“大无畏”，不怕艰难困苦，永久坚持的精神。红军的大无畏不怕牺牲的精神，永远激励着我们前进！</p><p>   长征是人类历史上艰苦奋斗精神的楷模。长征途中，红军将士面对的是一条条波涛汹涌的大河，一座座巍然耸立的雪山，一片片茫无涯际的草地，前有敌军，后有追兵，可就是在这“敌军围困万千重”的逆境中，红军转战两万五千里，终于从100万的敌人中杀出了一条生路。谱写出一曲曲动人的“永久奋斗”的革命乐章。</p><p>长征是充满着无私奉献精神的史诗。无论是难以自拔的沼泽，还是茫茫无际的</p><p>草地；无论是皑皑白雪，还是飞机大炮；无论是酷暑严寒，还是饥饿干渴……红军将士都抱定全心全意为人民服务的宗旨，以坚忍不拔的毅力，与穷凶极恶的敌人展开殊死搏斗，将生的希望让给别人，死的威胁留给自己。</p><p><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180725/1532508332791127.jpg" title="1532508332791127.jpg" alt="2.jpg"/></p><p>    一个国家，一个民族，乃至一个团体，只要有艰苦奋斗的精神，实事求是，无私奉献，就能够成就事业，创造辉煌。80年前的长征是这样，80年后的今天也是这样。</p><p>我们进行的社会主义现代化建设，是新的长征。走在新长征路上，我们应继承和发扬当年红军长征的精神，把长征这份宝贵的精神财富变成推动我们各项事业前进的巨大力量。红军长征的路是艰苦的、漫长的；新长征的路会更艰苦、更漫长。因此，我们回忆长征、纪念长征，就是要更好地继承和弘扬红军长征精神，把红军长征留给我们的宝贵精神财富一代一代传下去，万众一心、艰苦奋斗，争取社会主义现代化建设“新长征”的胜利。</p><p>    艰苦奋斗是中华民族的传统美德，是我们党领导和团结人民进行革命、建设和改革的强大精神动力。然而，有些党员认为生活水平提高了，没必要讲艰苦奋斗了，因此<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%B4%AA%E5%9B%BE%E5%AE%89%E9%80%B8" target="_blank">贪图安逸</a>、追求享乐，讲排扬、摆阔气，生活高标准、工作低要求，特别是有少数党员领导干部过着纸醉金迷的奢侈腐朽生活，甚至坠入了违法犯罪的深渊，如果这种现象任其不断扩大和蔓延，势必严重侵蚀党的肌体，破坏党群关系。所以，在新的形势下，要保持共产党员先进性，艰苦奋斗作风不能丢。</p><p><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180725/1532508340440525.jpg" title="1532508340440525.jpg" alt="3.jpg"/></p><p>    保持和发扬艰苦奋斗的作风，才能进一步坚定理想信念。共产主义理想和社会主义信念，是共产党人崇高的追求和强大的精神支柱。在革命战争年代，革命前辈在<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%BA%95%E5%86%88%E5%B1%B1" target="_blank">井冈山</a>如果不发扬以门板当床、稻草做被的艰苦奋斗作风，就难以点燃革命的星星之火；在长征路上如果不发扬爬雪山过草地、嚼草根吃树皮的艰苦奋斗作风，就难以使中国革命转危为安；在延安如果不发扬自力更生、奋发图强的艰苦奋斗作风，就难以取得抗战胜利；当年如果我们共产党人没有艰苦奋斗、勇于胜利的精神，就难以实现推翻三座大山、建立社会主义新中国的革命理想。同样，在改革开放的今天，我们仍然要靠艰苦奋斗精神战胜前进道路上的各种困难，并不断丰富艰苦奋斗的内涵，将崇高理想与现实工作统一起来，使之不断地与时俱进。</p><p><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%95%BF%E5%BE%81%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E/919848?fr=aladdin">https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%95%BF%E5%BE%81%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E/919848?fr=aladdin</a></p><p><br/></p><p>表现事例 周恩来</p><p>北伐长征</p><p><a href="https://baike.sogou.com/PicBooklet.v?relateImageGroupIds=1722998,1722999,1723001,1874611,1874612,1723002,1723018,1723006&lemmaId=5381621&now=https://pic.baike.soso.com/p/20131115/20131115154601-1207115923.jpg&type=1" title=""><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180725/1532508348445846.jpg" title="1532508348445846.jpg" alt="4.jpg"/></a><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border: 1px solid rgb(226, 226, 226);padding: 3px">周恩来</span></p><p>    1924年秋回国，在国共合作期间任广东黄埔军校政治部主任，国民革命军第一军政治部主任、第一军副党代表等职，并先后任中共广东区委员会委员长、常务委员兼军事部长，两次参加讨伐军阀<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=431632&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">陈炯明</a>的东征，创建了行之有效的<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=7974210&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">军队政治工作</a>制度。</p><p>    1927年3月在北伐的<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=348740&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">国民革命军</a>临近上海的情况下，领导上海工人第三次武装起义，赶走了驻守上海的北洋军阀部队。同年5月在<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=7068517&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">中共第五次全国代表大会</a>上当选为中央委员，在中共五届一中全会上当选为<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=68534187&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">中央政治局委员</a>。7月12日中共中央改组，他任<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=69657131&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">中共中央政治局</a>临时常务委员会委员。</p><p>国共合作全面破裂后，和贺龙、<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=202020&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">叶挺</a>、朱德、<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=51981&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">刘伯承</a>等一起于8月1日在江西南昌领导武装起义（南昌起义），任中共前敌委员会书记。</p><p>    1928年在<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=70011966&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">中共六届一中全会</a>上当选为中央政治局常务委员。后任<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=52387346&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">中央组织部</a>长、中央军委书记。为保证中共中央在上海秘密工作的安全，为联系和指导各地区共产党领导的武装斗争，为发展在国民党统治区的秘密工作，起到了重要作用。在这一阶段的大部分时间内，他实际上是中共中央的主要主持者。</p><p>    1931年12月，离开上海到中央革命根据地，先后任中央苏区中央局书记、中国工农红军总政治委员兼第一方面军总政治委员、中央革命军事委员会副主席。1933年春和朱德一起领导和指挥红军战胜了国民党军队对中央革命根据地的第四次“围剿”。1934年10月参加长征。</p><p>    1935年1月在贵州遵义举行的中共中央政治局扩大会议（遵义会议）上，支持毛泽东的正确主张，对实际确立以毛泽东为代表的新的中央的正确领导，起了关键性的作用，并继续被选为中央主要军事领导人之一。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;"> the spirit of the long march</p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;"> (1) background</p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180725/1532508325306474.jpg" title=" 1532508325306474.jpg" alt=" Mao Zhedong.Jpg"/></p><p> Long march spirit is China Communist Party created in twenty-five thousand in the long march of the revolutionary spirit. From 1934 to 1935 twenty-five thousand years experience China Red Army Long March is a miracle in the history of human warfare. The Red Army officers showed the cause of revolutionary ideals and extremely loyal, firm belief in the Long March, showed no fear of sacrifice, the courage to win the proletarian revolutionary spirit of optimism, showing the overall situation, strict discipline, close unity of noble character, created the great spirit of the long march. Which is: firm and indomitable courage, unremitting self-improvement. The most notable feature is &#34;not afraid of hardship, not afraid of death two&#34; revolutionary heroism. The long march spirit is the highest expression of the Chinese nation, the national spirit of unremitting self-improvement never yield in spite of reverses, is to ensure that our revolution and construction from victory to the powerful spirit.</p><p> October 1934 fifth campaign after the failure, the main force of the Red Army was forced to withdraw from the Jiangxi revolutionary base, to join forces with the two and six army to break through the enemy blockade along the four forces, loss of more than 50000 people. December,<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%BB%8E%E5%B9%B3%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%AE" target="_self"> the liping meeting</a> After the meeting, the Red Army changed the rendezvous plan, marching to the hinterland of Guizhou. In January 1935, the Red Army to attack<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%A8%84%E5%B1%B1%E5%85%B3" target="_self"> Loushanguan</a> , occupied the city of Zunyi, Political Bureau held an enlarged</p><p> The meeting, Mao Zedong in the central leadership also began to establish. After the meeting, the Red Army crossing Chishui river,<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%B7%A7%E6%B8%A1%E9%87%91%E6%B2%99%E6%B1%9F" target="_self"> Clever crossing Jinsha River</a> ,<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%BC%BA%E6%B8%A1%E5%A4%A7%E6%B8%A1%E6%B2%B3" target="_self"> make a force crossing of the Dadu river</a> And over the Jinshan folder. In June, joined the Red Army, began to fight with Zhang Guotao separatism, the left army through few people tread grass. Then, the red, the three army and military column to the north, to capture the natural barrier Lazikou, crossing<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%85%AD%E7%9B%98%E5%B1%B1" target="_self"> Six Panshan</a> Arrive, Wuqi and<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%99%95%E5%8C%97%E7%BA%A2%E5%86%9B" target="_self"> The Red Army in Northern Shaanxi</a> By joining the Central Red Army came to an end. In October 1936 China realignment of the first, second, Fourth Front Army in Gansu province Huining, announced the victory of the long march of the Red Army.</p><p> (2) definition</p><p> Willing to endure hardship, not afraid of<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%89%B0%E9%9A%BE%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD" target="_self"> Difficult revolution</a> Optimism and courage in battle,<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%97%A0%E5%9D%9A%E4%B8%8D%E6%91%A7" target="_self"> Carry all before one</a> The revolutionary heroism; to truth-seeking, independent innovation courage; good at unity, the overall situation of the collective. The theme is &#34;not afraid of hardship, not afraid of death two&#34;; its most notable feature is the revolutionary spirit of heroism. The long march spirit of the Chinese nation never yield in spite of reverses,<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%87%AA%E5%BC%BA%E4%B8%8D%E6%81%AF" target="_self"> Unremitting self-improvement</a> The highest expression of national spirit, is to ensure that our revolution and construction from weak to strong spiritual strength.</p><p><a></a><a></a><a></a>  </p><p> What is the spirit of the long march?</p><p>    <a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%95%BF%E5%BE%81/22312" target="_self"> long march</a> Is a model of Chinese national spirit of the refuse to be cowed or submit. Throughout the entire process of the long march: four Chishui River, clever crossing<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%87%91%E6%B2%99%E6%B1%9F" target="_self"> Jinsha River</a> Fly away;<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%B3%B8%E5%AE%9A%E6%A1%A5" target="_self"> Luding Bridge</a> , Dadu, climb mountains, over the grass...... A strategic change of direction, determine each of the strategic task, every battle victory, are all reflect the China Red Army soldiers &#34;fearless&#34;, not afraid of difficulties and hardships, adhere to the spirit of the permanent. The dauntless spirit of sacrifice, always inspire us forward!</p><p> Long march is a model of human history of the spirit of arduous struggle. On the Long March, the Red Army soldiers face is a roaring waves of the river, stands a mountain, a piece of grass in front of stretch to the horizon, the enemy, after the pursuers, but in this &#34;enemy siege my heavy&#34; in the face of adversity, the red army fought in twenty-five thousand, finally from 1 million enemies in a blaze let it go. Write a touching &#34;permanent struggle&#34; of the revolutionary movement.</p><p> The long march is filled with the spirit of selfless dedication of the epic. It is difficult to extricate itself from the swamp, or boundless</p><p> Grassland; whether snow, or aircraft artillery; both heat and cold, hunger or thirst...... The Red Army soldiers clung to the purpose of serving the people wholeheartedly, with firm and indomitable perseverance, launched a desperate struggle with the most vicious enemy, the hope of life to others, death threats to yourself.</p><p><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180725/1532508332791127.jpg" title=" 1532508332791127.jpg" alt=" 2.jpg"/></p><p> A country, a nation, or even a group, as long as the spirit of hard work, realistic, selfless dedication, to create brilliant achievements. 80 years ago, the long march is that, after 80 years today too.</p><p> The construction of socialist modernization, is the new long march. Go on the new Long March, we should inherit and carry forward the spirit of the long march of the Red Army, the valuable spiritual wealth into great power to promote the cause of our progress. The long march road is hard and long; the new long march road will be more difficult and more long. Therefore, we recall the long march to commemorate the Long March, it is necessary to better inherit and carry forward the spirit of the long march of the Red Army, the Red Army left us a valuable spiritual wealth from generation to generation, and struggle for the socialist modernization million people united as one man, the construction of the new Long March victory &#34;.</p><p> Hard struggle is the traditional virtue of Chinese nation, is a powerful spiritual force of our Party leadership and unity of the people in revolution, construction and reform. However, some party members that raised the standard of living, no need to speak so hard.<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%B4%AA%E5%9B%BE%E5%AE%89%E9%80%B8" target="_self"> Comfort</a> And the pursuit of pleasure, said Yang, put on the row, a high standard of living, low work requirements, especially a few leading cadres have a luxury decadent life, even fall into the abyss of crimes, if this phenomenon as it continues to expand and spread, it will seriously eroded the party&#39;s body, destroy the relationship between the party and the masses. So, in the new situation, to maintain a communist advanced sex, hard work style can not be lost.</p><p><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180725/1532508340440525.jpg" title=" 1532508340440525.jpg" alt=" 3.jpg"/></p><p> Maintain and carry forward the style of hard struggle, in order to further strengthen the ideals and beliefs. The communist ideal and belief in socialism, is the pursuit of lofty and powerful spiritual prop. During the revolutionary war, the revolutionary predecessors in<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%BA%95%E5%86%88%E5%B1%B1" target="_self"> Jinggang Mountains</a> If you do not carry forward the door when the bed is made of straw, the style of hard struggle, it is difficult to ignite the sparks of fire of the revolution; in March on the road if you do not carry forward the style of mountain climbing and over the grass, chewing roots and bark of hard work, it is difficult to make Chinese revolution through; in Yanan if you do not carry forward the style of self-reliance and hard work make efforts, it is difficult to obtain in the war when the Communist Party victory; if we did not work hard, brave spirit of victory, it is difficult to achieve, the establishment of the socialist new Chinese by the birth of the revolutionary ideal. Similarly, in today&#39;s reform and opening up, we still rely on the spirit of arduous struggle to overcome all difficulties on the road ahead, and constantly enrich the connotation of hard struggle, the lofty ideal and reality of unification, to continue to advance with the times.</p><p><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%95%BF%E5%BE%81%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E/919848?fr=aladdin"> Https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%95%BF%E5%BE%81%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E/919848 fr=aladdin?</a></p><p><br/></p><p> Performance of the case of Zhou Enlai</p><p> During the long march</p><p><a href="https://baike.sogou.com/PicBooklet.v?relateImageGroupIds=1722998,1722999,1723001,1874611,1874612,1723002,1723018,1723006&lemmaId=5381621&now=https://pic.baike.soso.com/p/20131115/20131115154601-1207115923.jpg&type=1" title=""><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180725/1532508348445846.jpg" title=" 1532508348445846.jpg" alt=" 4.jpg"/></a><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border: 1px solid rgb(226, 226, 226);padding: 3px"> Zhou Enlai</span></p><p> 1924 autumn home, director of the Political Department of the Guangdong Military Academy in Whampoa during the first KMT-CPC cooperation, director, Army Political Department of the National Revolutionary Army First Army Deputy Party and other staff, and has served as a member of the CPC Guangdong District Committee, standing committee member and Minister of military long, participated in the two Crusade in the valve<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=431632&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Chen</a> The Crusades, to create effective<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=7974210&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> The political work in the army</a> System.</p><p> March 1927 in the Northern Expedition<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=348740&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> the National Revolutionary Army</a> Near Shanghai, the leadership of the third Shanghai workers&#39; armed uprising, get rid of the troops stationed in Shanghai&#39;s northern warlords. In May of the same year<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=7068517&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> The Fifth National Congress of the CPC</a> Was elected as a member of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of China, in the first Plenary Session of the 5th CPC Central Committee was elected<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=68534187&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Member of the Political Bureau of the CPC Central Committee</a> . In July 12th he served as the CPC Central Committee reorganization.<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=69657131&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> The Political Bureau of the CPC Central Committee</a> A temporary member of the standing committee.</p><p> After a comprehensive breakdown of KMT-CPC cooperation, and He Long,<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=202020&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Ye Ting</a> Zhu De,<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=51981&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> one of the Ten Great Marshals</a> Together in August 1st in Jiangxi Nanchang led an armed uprising (Nanchang uprising), Secretary of the CPC front committee.</p><p> In 1928<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=70011966&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> The Communist Party of China in the first Plenary Session of the 6th CPC Central Committee</a> Was elected member of the Standing Committee of the Political Bureau of the central committee. Successor<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=52387346&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> The Central Organization Department</a> Long, Secretary of the Central Military commission. In order to ensure that the CPC Central Committee in Shanghai secret work safety, to contact and guide the regional leadership of the Communist Party of the armed struggle for the secret development work in the Kuomintang areas, played an important role. At this stage most of the time, he is actually the CPC Central Committee presided over the main.</p><p> December 1931, from Shanghai to the central revolutionary base, has served as secretary of the Central Council and members of the Central Soviet Red Army General Political China and First Army General Political Committee, vice chairman of the Central Revolutionary Military commission. The spring of 1933 and Zhu De with the leadership and command of the red army defeated the Kuomintang troops on the fourth &#34;encirclement and suppression of Central Revolutionary base&#34;. In March October 1934.</p><p> The Political Bureau of the CPC Central Committee meeting held in Guizhou in January 1935 Zunyi (Zunyi Conference), right advocate Mao Zedong&#39;s support for the actual establishment of correct leadership with Mao Zedong as the representative of the new central government, played a key role, and continue to be selected as one of the main leaders of the central military.</p><p><br/></p>', 479, 121, '');
