INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(41, '首页->不忘初心->红色岁月->精神->延安精神', 'Home Page->Past->Red years->spirit->the Yan&#39;an spirit', '1532509367', '2018-08-29', '00:04:46', '1', '<p>延安精神</p><p>（1）时代背景</p><p>延安精神是延安时期中国共产党及其领导的根据地军民在革命实践中所表现出来的一种积极向上的精神风貌和优良作风。在延安，中国共产党孕育了光照千秋的延安精神，在中国的革命和建设中发挥了巨大的精神动力作用。延安精神是中国共产党、也是中华民族的宝贵精神财富，它对<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=9380989" target="_blank">中国历史发展</a>进程产生着巨大和深远的影响。延安精神的主要内容是：坚定正确的政治方向，解放思想、实事求是的思想路线，全心全意为人民服务的根本宗旨，自力更生、艰苦奋斗的创业精神。<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/v484869.htm?fromTitle=%E5%BB%B6%E5%AE%89%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E#quote1">[1]</a></p><p> </p><p>（1）定义</p><p>1.自力更生、艰苦奋斗的创业精神</p><p>中国共产党是靠艰苦奋斗起家的，中国共产党和人民的事业是靠艰苦奋斗不断发展壮大的。回顾党的历史，从在上海成立到井冈山时期，从遵义会议到延安时期，从<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=345828" target="_blank">西柏坡</a>到夺取全国政权，从新中国成立到改革开放新时期，艰苦奋斗是工作作风，也是思想作风，是中国共产党的优良传统和政治本色，是凝聚党心民心、激励全党和全体人民为实现国家富强、民族振兴共同奋斗。</p><p><br/></p><p>2.全心全意为人民服务的精神</p><p>延安时期是中国共产党在中国局部地区建立人民政权并不断扩大执政区域的重要时期。中国共产党历来把为中国广大人民谋利益作为自己的根本宗旨，在延安时期又响亮地提出了“为人民服务”的口号并在全党认真实践。那时的陕甘宁边区政府，被誉为“民主的政治。”</p><p><br/></p><p>3.<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=370051" target="_blank">理论联系实际</a>、不断开拓创新的精神</p><p>延安时期是中国共产党科学总结正反两方面经验，成功地推进<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=701815" target="_blank">马克思主义中国化</a>、在理论上实现第一次历史性飞跃的时期。毛泽东同志的许多重要著作，如《<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=7778810&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">中国革命战争的战略问题</a>》、《<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=573468&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">实践论</a>》、《<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=4451639&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">矛盾论</a>》、《论持久战》、《<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=4209977&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">新民主主义论</a>》、《<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=6951752&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">论联合政府</a>》等，都是在延安时期完成的。</p><p><br/></p><p>4.实事求是的思想路线</p><p style="margin-bottom:15px;line-height:24px;background:white"><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333">用实事求是来概括中国共产党的思想路线，也是在延安时期。实践表明，只有解放思想，才能达到实事求是；只有实事求是，才是真正地解放思想。在新世纪新阶段，按照十六大的要求，切实做到发展要有新思路，改革要有新突破，开放要有新局面，各项工作要有新举措，这就叫作坚持解放思想，这也叫作坚持实事求是。</span></p><h1>汤恩佳</h1><p> </p><p>成长与成就 </p><p>    汤博士出身于广东三水悬壶济世的中医世家。祖父汤九义是祖传第四代中医，汤恩佳四岁开始学习《四书》、《五经》。1947年，年仅15岁的汤博士遵祖母之命怀揣一本《论语》，只身前往香港在其亲戚所办的一间染料厂当学徒。1951年，以当学徒时积攒的51元港币创业，自开一家小染料店——“佳成染料”。因汤博士待人至诚，重义守信，生意便日益兴隆。汤博士自小就产生了浓厚的爱国观念和民族情感，花了将近十年的时间去推国家染料，创办了“佳成三宝”。</p><p>    1978年改革开放，汤博士把握良机，以原有公司为基础，重组扩大为一家较大型规模的佳成染料有限公司，被称为香港的“染料大王”。此后，公司规模日益扩大。接着汤博士又创立了勤涌置业按揭有限公司、大宝山企业有限公司、永宝来有限公司和佳忠化工仓有限公司等四家新兴公司。</p><p>    身为孔教信徒的汤博士见到中华文化的优良传统“仁义礼智信”逐渐消失，作为爱国商人的他十分看不惯，也感到自己身上的责任。二十年前，事业成功的他从生意场上退了下来，把上了轨道的业务放下，专心从事孔子思想的研究工作，并要在全世界推广孔子的儒家思想。</p><p>    1992年，他接任香港孔教学院院长职位至今，将大部分精力投入到对孔子儒家思想的研究、宣传和对国内外孔子文化古迹的考察和资助。汤博士还经常走出国门，弘扬孔子儒家思想，并为促进国际文化交流，以一名民间外交使者自任。</p><p>   汤博士在弘扬孔子儒家思想等方面做出了令世人瞩目的贡献，“汤”、“汤夫子”有其理由。据不完全统计，他共获得200多个荣衔，并在全世界约900处地区宣扬孔家文化。五十多年来投身宣传孔子儒家思想，发表演讲辞和文章至今一千零六十篇，出版了一套《汤恩佳尊孔之旅环球演讲集合》著作（共二十一本），并在全世界捐献了500多座孔子像，他是一个集儒商、儒学、儒教于一身的传奇人物。</p><p>    汤博士在闲暇时间喜欢游泳，也喜欢打羽毛球，现在仍是香港羽毛总会会长。</p><p>    伴随汤博士的座右铭是：“业精于勤而荒于嬉。”</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> the Yan&#39;an spirit</p><p> (1) background</p><p> Yanan spirit is the period of Yanan China Communist Party and its leadership, according to a positive military and reflected in the practice of revolution spirit and excellent style. In Yanan, the Communist Party of China gave birth to light the spirit of Yanan will play a role in the great spiritual power of revolution and construction in the China. Yanan spirit is the Communist Party, China is precious spiritual wealth of the Chinese nation, for it<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=9380989" target="_self"> Chinese historical development</a> Has a great and far-reaching impact on the process. The main contents of the spirit of Yanan is a firm and correct political orientation, the ideological line of emancipating the mind, the fundamental purpose of serving the people wholeheartedly, self-reliance, hard work and entrepreneurial spirit.<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/v484869.htm?fromTitle=%E5%BB%B6%E5%AE%89%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E#quote1"> [1]</a></p><p>  </p><p> (1) definition</p><p> 1. the entrepreneurial spirit of self-reliance and hard work</p><p> The Communist Party is Chinese by hard work started, China Communist Party and the cause of people rely on hard work continue to thrive. Review the history of the party, from the set up in Shanghai to Jinggangshan, from Zunyi to Yanan during the meeting, from<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=345828" target="_self"> Xibaipo</a> To win the national government, from the new China establishment to the new period of reform and opening up, hard work is the style of work, but also the style of thinking, is a fine tradition of the Communist Party of China and political nature, is to unite the party and the people, inspire the whole Party and people to achieve national prosperity and rejuvenation of the nation together.</p><p><br/></p><p> 2. the spirit of serving the people wholeheartedly</p><p> Yanan period is an important period of the Communist Party of China in the local area China establishing people&#39;s regime and expanding the ruling area. The Communist Party has always been the Chinese for the majority of the people Chinese interests as its fundamental purpose, in the period of Yanan and made loud &#34;serve the people&#34; slogan and the practice in the party. Then the Shaanxi Gansu Ningxia border region government, known as the &#34;democratic politics.&#34;</p><p><br/></p><p> Three<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=370051" target="_self"> Theory and Practice</a> And the pioneering and innovative spirit</p><p> Yanan period is the Communist Party Chinese scientific summary of two aspects of positive and negative experiences, we have successfully<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=701815" target="_self"> The Marx doctrine of China</a> The first period, realize the historic leap in theory. Many important works of Comrade Mao Zedong, such as &#34;<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=7778810&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Strategic issues Chinese Revolutionary War</a> &#34;,&#34;<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=573468&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> The theory of practice</a> &#34;,&#34;<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=4451639&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> On contradiction</a> &#34;,&#34; on protracted war &#34;,&#34;<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=4209977&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> The theory of New Democracy</a> &#34;,&#34;<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=6951752&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> On the coalition government</a> &#34;That is done in the Yanan period.</p><p><br/></p><p> The 4. ideological line of seeking truth from facts</p><p style="margin-bottom:15px;line-height:24px;background:white"><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333"> To sum up with the realistic Chinese the ideological line of the Communist Party, but also in the Yanan period. Practice shows that only by emancipating the mind, to seek truth from facts; only the facts, truly emancipate the mind. In the new stage of the new century, in accordance with the sixteen requirements, to achieve new ideas for development, make new breakthroughs in reform, opening up to a new situation, take new initiatives, it is to insist on emancipating the mind, this is also called seeking truth from facts.</span></p><h1> Tong Yun Kai</h1><p>  </p><p> The growth and achievement of</p><p> Dr. Tang born Chinese family in Guangdong Sanshui xuanhujishi. Grandfather Tang Jiuyi is the ancestral fourth