INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(56, '首页->不忘初心->改革开放->人->袁隆平', 'Home Page->Past->Reform and Opening-up->people->Yuan Longping', '1532510463', '2018-08-29', '00:05:51', '1', '<p style="line-height:25px;background:white"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180814/1534221072310380.jpg" title="1534221072310380.jpg"/></p><p>人物简介：中国杂交水稻育种专家，中国<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=70549027&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">研究与发展</a>袁隆平是杂交水稻研究领域的开创者和带头人，致力于杂交水稻的研究，先后成功研发出“三系法”杂交 水稻、“两系法”杂交水稻、<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=69359557&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">超级杂交稻</a>一期、二期，与此同时，袁隆平提出并实施“<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=70331021&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">种三产四</a>丰产工程”，运用超级杂交稻的技术成果，出版中、英文专著6部，发表论文60余篇。  2017年7月，任青岛<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=100093491&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">海水稻</a>学院首席教授。2017年9月，袁隆平宣布一项剔除水稻中重金属镉的新成果。2018年5月28日，袁隆平海水稻团队——<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=156310687&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">青岛海水稻研究发展中心</a>和袁米农业科技有限公司共同启动“中华拓荒人计划”。杂交水稻的开创者，被誉为“世界杂交水稻之父”。<br/></p><p><br/></p>', '<p style="line-height:25px;background:white"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"></span></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180814/1534221072310380.jpg" title=" 1534221072310380.jpg"/></p><p> Biography: hybrid rice breeding expert Chinese, Chinese<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=70549027&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> research and development</a> Yuan Longping is a research field of hybrid rice pioneers and leaders, dedicated to the study of hybrid rice, has successfully developed the &#34;three line&#34; hybrid rice, &#34;two-line hybrid rice&#34;,<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=69359557&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Super hybrid rice</a> One, two, at the same time, Yuan Longping put forward and implemented&#34;<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=70331021&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Three four</a> High technology project &#34;, the results of the use of super hybrid rice, in English, published 6 monographs and published more than 60 papers. July 2017, Qingdao<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=100093491&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> The sea of rice</a> The chief professor. In September 2017, Yuan Longping announced the results of a new cadmium elimination in rice. In May 28, 2018, Yuan Longping rice water team<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=156310687&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Qingdao sea rice research and Development Center</a> And Yuan meters of agricultural science and technology limited company jointly launched the &#34;pioneer plan&#34;. The pioneer of hybrid rice, known as the &#34;father of hybrid rice in the world&#34;.<br/></p><p><br/></p>', 293, 122, '');
