INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(61, '首页->不忘初心->改革开放->精神->两弹一星', 'Home Page->Past->Reform and Opening-up->spirit->Two bombs and one satellite', '1532510896', '2018-08-29', '00:06:29', '1', '<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;">两弹一星</p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;">（1）时代背景</p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;">    “两弹一星”最初指原子弹、氢弹、人造卫星。“两弹”中的原子弹和氢弹后来合称核弹，另<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=8807503&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">一弹指</a>早期研发的导弹。后来“两弹一星”指导弹、核弹、人造卫星。</p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;">1960年11月5日，中国仿制的第一枚导弹发射成功，1964年10月16日15时中国第一颗原子弹爆炸成功，使中国成为第五个有原子弹的国家；1967年6月17日上午8时中国第一颗氢弹空爆试验成功；1970年4月24日21时中国第一颗人造卫星发射成功，使中国成为第五个发射人造卫星的国家。中国的“两弹一星”是20世纪下半叶中华民族创建的辉煌伟业。</p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;">    20世纪50年代、60年代是极不寻常的时期，当时面对严峻的国际形势，为抵制帝国主义的武力威胁和<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=37300&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">核讹诈</a>，50年代中期，以<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=65544676&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">毛泽东</a>同志为核心的第一代党中央领导集体。根据当时的国际形势，为了保卫国家安全、维护世界和平，高瞻远瞩，果断地作出了独立自主研制“两弹一星”的战略决策。大批优秀的科技工作者，包括许多在国外已经有杰出成就的科学家，以身许国，怀着对新中国的满腔热爱，响应党和国家的召唤，义无反顾地投身到这一神圣而<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=63414888&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">伟大的事业</a>中来。他们和参与“两弹一星”研制工作的广大干部、工人、解放军指战员一起，在当时国家经济、技术基础薄弱和工作条件十分艰苦的情况下，自力更生，发愤图强，完全依靠<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=142470555&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">自己的力量</a>，用较少的投入和较短的时间，突破了核弹、导弹和人造卫星等尖端技术，取得了举世瞩目的辉煌成就。</p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;">    早在20世纪50年代，毛泽东就发出“我们也要搞人造卫星”的号召，我国航天技术从无到有、从小到大地发展起来。</p><p style="text-align:center"><a href="https://baike.sogou.com/PicBooklet.v?imageGroupId=2766806&relateImageGroupIds=2605990,2766806&lemmaId=451023" title=""><span style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); border: 1px solid rgb(226, 226, 226); padding: 3px;"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180725/1532510893483629.jpg" title="1532510893483629.jpg" alt="9.jpg"/></span></a></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; background: white; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border: 1px solid rgb(226, 226, 226);padding: 3px">两弹一星</span><br/></p><p>50年代中期，刚刚诞生的新中国百废待兴，面对国际上严峻的核讹诈形势和军备竞赛的发展趋势，以毛泽东同志为核心的党中央第一代领导集体毅然作出发展导弹、核弹、<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=56596&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">人造地球卫星</a>，突破国防尖端技术的战略决策。1956年，研制导弹、原子弹被列入中国的12年科学技术发展规划。仅用4年时间，1960年中国就成功地发射了第一枚自主研制的导弹。1964年，中国研制的第一颗原子弹爆炸成功，1967年又爆炸成功第一颗氢弹。1970年，我国用<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=536297&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">长征号运载火箭</a>，成功地发射中国的第一颗人造卫星-- 东方红一号 ，成为继苏联、美国、法国、日本之后，世界上第五个能独立发射人造地球卫星的国家。从此之后，中国的国防科技工业不断发展壮大，先后掌握了 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=48029" target="_blank">中子弹</a>设计技术和核武器小型化技术，研制和发射了各种型号的战略战术导弹和 运载火箭，潜艇<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=85487362&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">水下发射</a>成功，发射多颗<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=601115&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">返回式卫星</a>、 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=12091" target="_blank">地球同步轨道</a>及太阳同步轨道卫星。“两弹一星”不仅为我们建立 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=128335419" target="_blank">战略导弹部队</a>提供了装备技术保障，增强了我军在高技术条件下的防御能力和作战能力，而且带动了中国高技术及其产业的发展，促进了经济建设和科技进步。“两弹一星”事业所取得的巨大成就，是中国人民挺直腰杆站起来的重要标志，极大地鼓舞了全党全军全国人民的斗志，增强了民族凝聚力，激发了振兴中华的爱国热情。正如邓小平同志曾经指出的那样：“如果六十年代以来中国没有原子弹、氢弹，没有发射卫星，中国就不能叫有重要影响的大国，就没有现在这样的国际地位。这些东西反映一个民族的能力，也是一个民族、一个国家兴旺发达的标志。”</p><p>（1） 定义</p><p> </p><p>“两弹一星”是新中国伟大成就的象征，是中华民族的骄傲。在全国各族人民喜迎新中国50华诞之际，党中央、国务院、中央军委隆重表彰为我国“两弹一星”事业作出卓越贡献的功臣。我们向功臣们表示热烈的祝贺，向参与“两弹一星”事业的所有科学技术人员、管理人员、工人和人民解放军指战员表示崇高的敬意，向为了这一事业献身的同志们表示深切的怀念。</p><p><a></a>发扬精神</p><p>我们要学习“两弹一星”功臣们勇于探索、勇于创新的精神。在“两弹一星”的研制过程中，我们看到了高水平的<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=66316876&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">技术跨越</a>。从原子弹到氢弹，我们仅用两年零八个月的时间，比美国、前苏联、法国所用的时间要短得多。在导弹和卫星的研制中所采用的新技术、新材料、新工艺、新方案，在许多方面跨越了传统的技术阶段。“两弹一星”是中国人民创造活力的产物。"两弹一星"精神表述：热爱祖国、无私奉献、自力更生、艰苦奋斗、大力协同、勇于攀登。</p><p>21世纪的国际科技和经济的竞争，从根本上讲是高科技、高素质人才的竞争，是知识创新、技术创新的竞争。要把建设有 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=499828" target="_blank">中国特色社会主义</a>事业推向前进，要在激烈的国际竞争中得到发展，就要努力学习和发扬功臣们的爱国主义精神、无私奉献精神和勇于创新的精神，团结一心，励精图治，不畏艰险，勇往直前！</p><p>《<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=115794&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank"> 人民日报</a>》 (1999年09月19日第2版)</p><p><a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=7789403&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">两弹一星精神</a>——“热爱祖国、无私奉献，自力更生、艰苦奋斗，大力协同、勇于登攀。”</p><p>两弹一星精神是中华人民共和国诸多“精神”及政治语汇中的一个，象征了在欠缺良好环境下，从事科学技术开发研究的精神，也是科教兴国政策的开端。</p><p>对于中国而言，两弹一星是在非常艰苦、没有外援的环境下所开发出来的成果。而“两弹一星”精神象征了中华民族自力更生、在社会主义之下集中力量从事科学开发研究，并创造“科技奇迹”的态度与过程，组合的元素则为“爱国主义”、“集体主义”、“社会主义”与“科学精神”，并可以衍生至“科技创新”“知识经济”等领域。</p><p>"两弹一星”精神，是爱国主义、集体主义、社会主义精神和科学精神的活生生体现，是中国人民在20世纪为中华民族创造的新的宝贵精神财富。我<span style=";font-family:宋体">们要继续发扬光大这一</span>伟大精神，使之成为全国各族人民在现代化建设道路上奋勇开拓的巨大推动力量。</p><p>"两弹一星”精神，当成政治语汇可以用在科技发展、高等教育、人才培育等领域上，例如：“用两弹一星精神创建一流大学”、“用两弹一星精神开发信息产业”等。</p><p>(3)其著名元勋人物</p><p><a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=332098" target="_blank">王淦昌</a>、 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=86253" target="_blank">邓稼先</a>、 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=2205773" target="_blank">赵九章</a>、 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=7776770" target="_blank">姚桐斌</a>、 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=62961352" target="_blank">钱骥</a>、 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=197951" target="_blank">钱三强</a>、 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=238128" target="_blank">郭永怀</a>。</p><p><a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=237588" target="_blank">钱学森</a>、 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=69545872" target="_blank">吴自良</a>、 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=406969" target="_blank">陈芳允</a>、 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=406981" target="_blank">杨嘉墀</a>、 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=332608" target="_blank">彭桓武</a>、 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=168860" target="_blank">朱光亚</a>、 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=8898127" target="_blank">黄纬禄</a>、 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=591811" target="_blank">王大珩</a>、 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=5157014" target="_blank">屠守锷</a>、 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=639125" target="_blank">陈能宽</a>。</p><p><a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=6837670" target="_blank">程开甲</a>、 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=72946" target="_blank">王希季</a>、 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=7495263" target="_blank">孙家栋</a>、 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=86375" target="_blank">任新民</a>、 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=193875" target="_blank">周光召</a>、 <a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=198189" target="_blank">于敏</a>。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;"> Two bombs and one satellite</p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;"> (1) background</p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;"> &#34;Two bombs and one satellite&#34; means the first atomic bomb, the hydrogen bomb and artificial satellite. &#34;Two bombs&#34; in the atomic bomb and hydrogen bomb bomb later called the other.<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=8807503&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> a flick of the finger</a> The early development of missile. Later &#34;two bombs and one satellite&#34; guidance bomb, bomb, satellite.</p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;"> In November 5, 1960, China imitation of the first missile was successfully launched in October 16, 1964 15, when Chinese successfully exploded its first atomic bomb, which Chinese has become the fifth atomic bomb in the world; China June 17, 1967 morning 8 when the first hydrogen bomb blast experiment success; April 24, 1970 21 Chinese first satellite was successfully launched, the China became the fifth to launch an artificial satellite the country. China &#34;two bombs and one satellite&#34; is the second half of twentieth Century, the Chinese nation created brilliant albert.</p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;"> 1950s, 60s is a very unusual period, when facing the serious international situation, as the threat of force and resist imperialist<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=37300&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Nuclear blackmail</a> In mid 50s,<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=65544676&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Mao Zedong</a> At the core of the first generation of central collective leadership of the party. According to the international situation, in order to safeguard national security, safeguard world peace, made a resolute look far ahead from a high plane, independent development strategy of &#34;two bombs and one satellite&#34;. A large number of outstanding scientific and technological workers, including many in foreign countries have the outstanding achievements of scientists, the body Xu, filled with love for the new China, in response to the party and the country&#39;s call, hesitate to plunge into the sacred<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=63414888&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Great cause</a> In. They participate in the &#34;two bombs and one satellite&#34; of the research work of the cadres and workers, the PLA officers and men together, at the time of the country&#39;s economic and technological foundation is weak and the working conditions are very difficult circumstances, completely rely on self-reliance, strive for progress with determination.<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=142470555&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Your strength</a> , with less investment and shorter time, break the bomb, missiles and satellites and other cutting-edge technology, has achieved a brilliant success.</p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;"> In early 1950s, Mao Zedong issued a &#34;we will engage satellites&#34; appeal, the earth from space technology in our country, to develop from scratch.</p><p style="text-align:center"><a href="https://baike.sogou.com/PicBooklet.v?imageGroupId=2766806&relateImageGroupIds=2605990,2766806&lemmaId=451023" title=""><span style="color: rgb(51, 102, 204); border: 1px solid rgb(226, 226, 226); padding: 3px;"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180725/1532510893483629.jpg" title=" 1532510893483629.jpg" alt=" 9.jpg"/></span></a></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 24px; background: white; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);border: 1px solid rgb(226, 226, 226);padding: 3px"> Two bombs and one satellite</span><br/></p><p> In mid 50s, the new Chinese a thousand things wait to be done just born, facing the development trend of the international situation and the severe nuclear blackmail in an arms race, with Comrade Mao Zedong as the core of the first generation central collective leadership decided to make a nuclear bomb, missile development,<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=56596&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Artificial earth satellite</a> Strategic breakthrough, sophisticated national defense technology. In 1956, the missile and atomic bomb was included in the China 12 year science and technology development planning. In just 4 years, 1960 China successfully launched the first self-developed missile. In 1964, China developed the first atomic bomb successfully, and successfully exploded the first hydrogen bomb in 1967. In 1970, China<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=536297&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> The long march rocket</a> The China, successfully launched the first artificial satellite, Dongfanghong, become after the Soviet Union, the United States, France, Japan, the world&#39;s fifth independent national launch of sputnik. Since then, the continuous development of the national defense science and technology industry Chinese grow, has mastered the<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=48029" target="_self"> In the bullet</a> The design of nuclear weapons technology and miniaturization technology, developed and launched various types of strategic and tactical missiles and rockets, submarine<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=85487362&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Underwater launch</a> Successful launch multiple satellites<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=601115&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Return satellite</a> And<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=12091" target="_self"> Geosynchronous orbit</a> And the sun synchronous orbit satellite. &#34;Two bombs and one satellite&#34; not only establish for us<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=128335419" target="_self"> The strategic missile forces</a> Provide equipment and technical support, enhance our army in the condition of high technology defense capabilities and combat capability, but also led to the development of China high technology and its industry, promoting the economic construction and the progress of science and technology. &#34;The great achievement made in the cause of two bombs and one satellite&#34;, is an important symbol of people&#39;s China upright stand up, greatly inspired the whole army and the people&#39;s morale, enhance national cohesion, stimulate the patriotic enthusiasm of the rejuvenation of the Chinese nation. As Comrade Deng Xiaoping once pointed out: &#34;if since 60s Chinese no atomic bomb, hydrogen bomb, satellite launch, China can not be called have an important impact on the country, there is no such international position now. These things reflect the ability of a nation, but also a symbol of a nation, the prosperity of a country.&#34;</p><p> (1) definition</p><p>  </p><p> &#34;Two bombs and one satellite&#34; is a symbol of the new Chinese great achievements, is the pride of the Chinese nation. People of all nationalities in the country to celebrate the new China 50 anniversary, the CPC Central Committee and the State Council and the Central Military Commission commended made outstanding contributions to China&#39;s &#34;two bombs and one satellite&#34; in the cause of the hero. We express our warm congratulations to the people, to participate in the &#34;two bombs and one satellite&#34; the cause of all scientific and technical personnel, management personnel, workers and the people&#39;s Liberation Army paid tribute to, in order to devotion to that cause Comrades expressed deep nostalgia.</p><p><a></a> Carry forward the spirit of</p><p> We should learn from the &#34;two bombs and one satellite&#34; hero who dare to explore and innovative spirit. In the development process of two bombs and one satellite &#34;, we see a high level<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=66316876&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Technological leapfrogging</a> . From the atomic bomb to the bomb, we only use the time in two years and eight months, with the United States, than that of the former Soviet Union, France&#39;s time is much shorter. Used in missile and satellite in new technology, new materials, new technology and new programs in many ways across the stage of traditional technology. &#34;Two bombs and one satellite&#34; is a product of Chinese people&#39;s creativity. &#34;Two bombs and one satellite&#34; spiritual expression: love the motherland, selfless dedication, self-reliance, hard work, strong coordination and the courage to climb.</p><p> In twenty-first Century the international economic and technological competition, is fundamentally the high-quality talents of high-tech, competition, is the innovation of knowledge and technology competition. The construction of<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=499828" target="_self"> Chinese socialism</a> Pushing forward the cause, to develop in the fierce international competition, we should strive to learn and carry forward the heroes patriotic spirit, selfless dedication and innovative spirit, solidarity, good governance, Buweijianxian, courage!</p><p> &#34;<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=115794&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> People&#39;s daily</a> &#34;(09 1999 19 August second edition)</p><p><a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=7789403&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Two bombs and one satellite spirit</a> &#34;Love the motherland, selfless dedication, self-reliance and hard work, cooperation, the courage to climb.&#34;</p><p> Two bombs and one satellite spirit is a People&#39;s Republic of China many &#34;spirit&#34; and the political vocabulary, a symbol of the lack of a good environment, engaged in technology research and development of scientific spirit, the beginning is the policy of rejuvenating the country through science and.</p><p> For China, two bombs and one satellite is developed in very hard, no outside environment achievements. &#34;Two bombs and one satellite&#34; symbol