INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(71, '首页->继续前行->新时代新星->人->李想', 'Home Page->Future->A new era of star->people->Li Xiang', '1532512107', '2018-08-29', '00:07:34', '1', '<p style="text-align:center"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180814/1534221243909789.jpg" title="1534221243909789.jpg" alt="李想1.jpg"/></p><p>1981年10月出生于河北石家庄，80后企业家代表人物。曾先后创立泡泡网、 <a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%B1%BD%E8%BD%A6%E4%B9%8B%E5%AE%B6/81714" target="_blank">汽车之家</a>，现任车和家创始人及CEO。1998年还在上<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%AD/1935" target="_blank">高中</a>的李想就开始做<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99" target="_blank">个人网站</a>，2000年注册<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%B3%A1%E6%B3%A1%E7%BD%91/6123713" target="_blank">泡泡网</a>并开始运营，仅凭借着自己对IT产品的一腔热爱和滚雪球式的资本积累，高中学历的李想让<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%B3%A1%E6%B3%A1%E7%BD%91/6123713" target="_blank">泡泡网</a>在中国互联网行业中独树一帜。2005年，李想带领团队从IT产品向汽车业扩张，创建<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%B1%BD%E8%BD%A6%E4%B9%8B%E5%AE%B6/81714" target="_blank">汽车之家</a>网站。目前，汽车之家现已成长为全球<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E9%87%8F/392852" target="_blank">访问量</a>最大的汽车网站，2012年底，汽车之家实现了月度覆盖用户8000万。2013年12月11日，李想带领汽车之家在美国纽约证劵交易所成功上市。2015年6月李想卸任总裁，继续担任董事股东。 2015年7月，李想创办<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%BD%A6%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%B6" target="_blank">车和家</a>。车和家定位于未来智能交通服务商，致力于打造人人可以轻松购买、使用的智能电动车。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p style="text-align:center"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180814/1534221243909789.jpg" title=" 1534221243909789.jpg" alt=" Li Xiang 1.jpg"/></p><p> Born in Hebei in October 1981 in Shijiazhuang, 80 entrepreneurs representative. Who has founded pcpop.com,<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%B1%BD%E8%BD%A6%E4%B9%8B%E5%AE%B6/81714" target="_self"> Car home</a> The current car, and founder and CEO. In 1998<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%AD/1935" target="_self"> high school</a> Li Xiang began to do<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99" target="_self"> Personal website</a> Registered in 2000,<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%B3%A1%E6%B3%A1%E7%BD%91/6123713" target="_self"> Pcpop.com</a> And begin operations, only by virtue of their capital IT product of a cavity love and snowball accumulation, senior high school, Li Xiangrang<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%B3%A1%E6%B3%A1%E7%BD%91/6123713" target="_self"> Pcpop.com</a> In China become an independent school in the Internet industry. In 2005, Li Xiang led the team to expand from IT products to the automotive industry, create<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%B1%BD%E8%BD%A6%E4%B9%8B%E5%AE%B6/81714" target="_self"> Car home</a> Web site. At present, the car home has grown into the world<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E9%87%8F/392852" target="_self"> Visits</a> The largest car website, by the end of 2012, the car home users monthly coverage of 80 million. In December 11, 2013, Li Xiang led the car home successfully listed on the New York stock exchange. Li Xiang stepped down as president in June 2015, continue to serve on the board of shareholders. July 2015, founder of Li Xiang<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%BD%A6%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%B6" target="_self"> The car and home</a> . The car and home located in the future intelligent transportation service provider, is committed to creating everyone can easily purchase and use of intelligent electric vehicle.</p><p><br/></p>', 344, 148, '');
