INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(76, '首页->继续前行->新时代新星->人->陈欧', 'Home Page->Future->A new era of star->people->Ou Chen', '1532512359', '2018-08-29', '00:07:44', '1', '<p style="text-align:center"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180814/1534221481933505.jpg" title="1534221481933505.jpg" alt="陈欧2.jpg"/></p><p>1983年2月4日出生于四川德阳，中国企业家、<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%81%9A%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%98%E5%93%81/3749691" target="_blank">聚美优品</a><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%88%9B%E5%A7%8B%E4%BA%BA/36538" target="_blank">创始人</a>兼<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/CEO/38500" target="_blank">CEO</a>。16岁留学<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1/145065" target="_blank">新加坡</a>就读<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%8D%97%E6%B4%8B%E7%90%86%E5%B7%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6/2134168" target="_blank">南洋理工大学</a>，大学期间曾成功创办在线游戏平台GG-Game。26岁获得美国斯坦福大学MBA学位，2009年回国创业，迅速成为中国80后青年的创业<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%A6%9C%E6%A0%B7/33808" target="_blank">榜样</a>。2012年、2013年，陈欧两次荣登<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%A6%8F%E5%B8%83%E6%96%AF/301065" target="_blank">福布斯</a>中文版评出的“中国30位30岁以下创业者名单”，并荣获“2014年中国互联网十大风云人物”称号。 2012年陈欧为公司拍摄的“我为自己代言”系列广告大片引起80后、90后强烈共鸣，在新浪微博掀起“<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%99%88%E6%AC%A7%E4%BD%93/5808485" target="_blank">陈欧体</a>”模仿热潮 [5-6]<a> </a>。2014年5月16日，<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%81%9A%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%98%E5%93%81/3749691" target="_blank">聚美优品</a>正式在美国<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%BA%BD%E7%BA%A6%E8%AF%81%E5%88%B8%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%89%80/271637" target="_blank">纽约证券交易所</a>挂牌上市，市值超过35亿美元。陈欧成为纽交所220余年历史上最年轻的上市公司<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/CEO/38500" target="_blank">CEO</a> [7]<a> </a> ，其所持股份市值超过11亿美元。 2015年，陈欧以11亿美元获得亚洲十大年轻富豪第六名。  </p><p><br/></p>', '<p style="text-align:center"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180814/1534221481933505.jpg" title=" 1534221481933505.jpg" alt=" Chen ou 2.jpg"/></p><p> February 4, 1983 born in Sichuan, Deyang, Chinese entrepreneurs,<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%81%9A%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%98%E5%93%81/3749691" target="_self"> Jumei.com</a><a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%88%9B%E5%A7%8B%E4%BA%BA/36538" target="_self"> Founder</a> And<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/CEO/38500" target="_self"> CEO</a> . The 16 year old students<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1/145065" target="_self"> Singapore</a> Attend school<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%8D%97%E6%B4%8B%E7%90%86%E5%B7%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6/2134168" target="_self"> Nanyang Technology University</a> During the University, has successfully established the online gaming platform GG-Game. At the age of 26 from the Stanford University MBA, 2009 home business, quickly became the Chinese 80 youth entrepreneurship<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%A6%9C%E6%A0%B7/33808" target="_self"> example</a> . 2012, 2013, Chen Ou two tops<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%A6%8F%E5%B8%83%E6%96%AF/301065" target="_self"> Forbes</a> Chinese version gave &#34;Chinese 30 entrepreneurs under 30 years old list, and won the&#34; 2014 Chinese Internet ten influential man &#34;title. In 2012 Chen Ou into filming &#34;I speak for themselves&#34; series of large advertising by 80, 90 strong resonance, set off in the Sina micro-blog&#34;<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%99%88%E6%AC%A7%E4%BD%93/5808485" target="_self"> Chen EC</a> &#34;Imitation boom [5-6]<a>  </a> . May 16, 2014,<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%81%9A%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%98%E5%93%81/3749691" target="_self"> Jumei.com</a> The official in the United States<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%BA%BD%E7%BA%A6%E8%AF%81%E5%88%B8%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%89%80/271637" target="_self"> New York stock exchange</a> Listing, the market value of more than $3 billion 500 million. Chen Ou NYSE became the youngest 220 years of listed companies<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/CEO/38500" target="_self"> CEO</a> [7]<a>  </a> , the st