INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(86, '首页->继续前行->共创地球村->一带一路->新丝绸之路', 'Home Page->Future->To create a global village->The Belt and Road->The new Silk Road', '1532513454', '2018-08-29', '00:08:20', '1', '<p style="background: white; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">新丝绸之路</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180725/1532513445790088.jpg" title="1532513445790088.jpg" alt="12.jpg"/></span></strong></p><p>它将充分依靠中国与有关国家既有的双多边机制，借助既有的、行之有效的区域合作平台，一带一路旨在借用古代丝绸之路的历史符号，高举和平发展的旗帜，积极发展与沿线国家的经济合作伙伴关系，共同打造政治互信、经济融合、文化包容的<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=83454787&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">利益共同体</a>、<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=73721208&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_blank">命运共同体</a>和责任共同体。</p><p>相关合作：“一带一路"经济区开放后，承包工程项目突破3000个。</p><p>我国企业共对“一带一路”相关的49个国家进行了直接投资，投资额同比增长18.2%。2015年，我国承接“一带一路”相关国家服务外包合同金额178.3亿美元，执行金额121.5亿美元，同比分别增长42.6%和23.45%。2018年1月25日，商务部发布的数据显示，“一带一路”经贸合作取得明显成效，2017年我国与沿线国家贸易额达7.4万亿元人民币，同比增长17.8%。“一带一路”沿线国家交融汇通，绝大多数国家都有改造升级国内铁路系统的需求，而中国高铁技术方面位居世界前列，强大的实力值得信任，同时拥有无可比拟的价格优势，中国高铁将成为中国在“一带一路”上的重要基石。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p style="background: white; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"> The new Silk Road</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180725/1532513445790088.jpg" title=" 1532513445790088.jpg" alt=" 12.jpg"/></span></strong></p><p> It will fully rely on Chinese with relevant countries existing bilateral and multilateral mechanisms, with the existing and effective platform for regional cooperation, the historical symbol The Belt and Road to borrow the ancient Silk Road of peaceful development, hold high the banner of active development and along the country&#39;s economic partnership to jointly build political trust, economic and cultural integration inclusive<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=83454787&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> The interests of the community</a> ,<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=73721208&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Community with a shared future</a> And the responsibility of the community.</p><p> Related cooperation: &#34;economic zones open The Belt and Road&#34; after the project breakthrough 3000.</p><p> China&#39;s enterprises in 49 countries related to &#34;The Belt and Road&#34; of direct investment, investment grew 18.2%. In 2015, China to undertake the &#34;The Belt and Road&#34; national service outsourcing contract amount of $17 billion 830 million, the implementation of the amount of $12 billion 150 million, an increase of 42.6% and 23.45% respectively. In January 25, 2018, the Ministry of Commerce released data show, &#34;The Belt and Road&#34; economic and trade cooperation has made remarkable achievements in 2017, China and the countries along the trade amounted to 7 trillion and 400 billion yuan, an increase of 17.8%. &#34;The Belt and Road along the country&#39;s blend of Huitong, the vast majority of countries have the upgrading of domestic railway system, and China high-speed rail technology in the world, strong strength, trust, and have There is nothing comparable to this price advantage, Chinese high iron will be in the&#34; The Belt and Road on China foundation.</p><p><br/></p>', 316, 89, '');
