INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(91, '首页->继续前行->共创地球村->地球村->地球村', 'Home Page->Future->To create a global village->global village->global village', '1532513743', '2018-08-29', '00:08:40', '1', '<p style=";background:white"></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180814/1534221648503445.jpg" title="1534221648503445.jpg"/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>地球村<br/></p><p>    地球村是说地球虽然很大，但是由于信息传递越来越方便，大家交流就像在一个小村子里面一样便利，就称地球这个大家庭为“地球村”了。地球村概念的产生更直观的表现人民需要和平世界的愿望。无论肤色、无论种族，人人平等到只是一个村落中的一份子。</p><p>相关信息：</p><p>（1）北京地球村、世界自然基金会、自然之友、中国民促会、中国环境文化促进会等9家民间环保组织在北京联合发起“26度空调”节能行动，呼吁在6月26日至9月9．6日期间，办公楼、饭店、商场等公共场所空调温度调至26℃。</p><p>（2）自然资源保护协会（NRDC）联合瑞士top10节能中心，碳阻迹、创绿研究院、世界自然基金会（WWF）、德国国际合作机构（GIZ）、能源与交通创新中心（iCET）、中华环保联合会、青年应对气候变化行动网络（CYCAN）、落基山研究所（RMI）、交通与发展政策研究所（ITDP）、绿色创新发展中心（iGDP）等多家环保和可持续发展组织呼吁全社会响应国家绿色发展号召、推动节能工作深入开展。在能源供应较为宽松的情况下，不能放松，更要狠抓节能，为保卫蓝天做贡献。</p><p>（3）山西全省30多家社会公益组织、大学生环保社团以及企业单位联合倡议，发起“美丽山西：开启我的60+生活从回归自然开始”地球一小时倡议活动。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p style=";background:white"></p><p style="text-align:center"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180814/1534221648503445.jpg" title=" 1534221648503445.jpg"/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p> global village<br/></p><p> Global village is that the earth is very big, but because of the transmission of information more convenient, everyone exchanges like the inside of a small village called Earth as convenient, the family as a &#34;global village&#34;. The concept of global village has a more intuitive performance needs of the people desire peace in the world. Regardless of color, regardless of race, everyone is equal to only a part of a village in the.</p><p> Related information:</p><p> (1) global village of Beijing, WWF, friends of nature, China hkdf, China Environmental Culture Promotion Association and other 9 environmental NGOs in Beijing jointly launched the &#34;26 air conditioning&#34; such action, called for in June 26th to September 9.6, office buildings, hotels, shopping malls and other public places, air temperature to 26 DEG C.</p><p> (2) Natural Resources Protection Association (NRDC) combined with Swiss TOP10 energy conservation center, carbon resistance trace, green Research Institute, the World Wildlife Fund (WWF), the German Agency for International Cooperation (GIZ), Innovation Center for energy and transportation (iCET), China Environment Federation, Youth Climate Action Network (CYCAN) and the Rocky Mountain Institute (RMI), transportation and Development Policy Research Institute (ITDP), green innovation and Development Center (iGDP) and a number of environmental protection and sustainable development of the organization called on the whole society in response to the national call for green development, promote energy conservation work thorough development. Can not relax in the energy supply more relaxed situation, more attention should be paid to energy saving, contribute to defending the blue sky.</p><p> (3) Shanxi province&#39;s more than 30 social welfare organizations, environmental groups and college students enterprises joint initiative, launched the &#34;beautiful Shanxi: open my 60+ life from nature to&#34; earth hour campaign.</p><p><br/></p>', 377, 146, '');
