INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(100, '首页->继续前行->共创地球村->环保政策', 'Home Page->Future->To create a global village->Environmental protection policy', '1532514275', '2018-07-25', '18:24:35', '1', '<p>首页->继续前行->共创地球村->环保政策</p>', '<p> Move on - &#62; &#62; &#62; &#62; to create a global village environmental protection policy</p>', 467, 55, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(101, '首页->继续前行->共创地球村->环保政策->环保政策', 'Home Page->Future->To create a global village->Environmental protection policy->Environmental protection policy', '1532514664', '2018-08-29', '00:09:13', '1', '<p style="text-align:center"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180820/1534774023645716.jpg" title="1534774023645716.jpg"/></p><p><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180820/1534774023474159.jpg" title="1534774023474159.jpg"/></p><p>    2013年9月7日，习近平总书记在哈萨克斯坦纳扎尔巴耶夫大学发表演讲并回答学生们提出的问题，在谈到环境保护问题时他指出：“我们既要绿水青山，也要金山银山。宁要绿水青山，不要金山银山，而且绿水青山就是金山银山。”（来源：人民网）</p><p>    近年来，我国愈发关注环境监测网络的一体化、集成化构建，并且严厉打击环境监测数据造假行为，将该产业拉进了全民监管视野内。无论是技术的革新，还是监测点的铺设，或者环境监测设备的调试升级，都推动了我国环境监测体系的成熟进程。</p><p>    日前，生态环境监测质量监督检查三年行动计划发布，监管到人、监管到事、监管到单、监管到数据、监管到细分责任，意义重大。按照相关负责人的说法，三年行动计划针对目前环境监测领域一些突出矛盾重点解决，全面覆盖监测机构、排污单位以及运维机构三类主体。可以说，这将是层层压实环保责任，威慑污染行为又一有效措施。</p><p>    生态环境部监测司有关负责人回应，三年行动将按照“双随机，一公开”的原则分3年完成。到2020年，基本实现健全的生态环境监测数据质量保障责任体系，有效遏制数据弄虚作假行为，并且形成“不敢假、不想假、不愿假”的良好氛围。（来源：中国环保网）</p><p><br/></p>', '<p style="text-align:center"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180820/1534774023645716.jpg" title=" 1534774023645716.jpg"/></p><p><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180820/1534774023474159.jpg" title=" 1534774023474159.jpg"/></p><p> September 7, 2013, general secretary Xi Jinping Steiner Zal in Kazakhstan Nazarbayev University speech and answered questions posed by students, pointing out that he talked about environmental problems: &#34;we should not only beautiful scenery, also jinshanyinshan. Nanjing to beautiful scenery, beautiful scenery and is not gold and silver, gold and silver.&#34; (source: people.com.cn)</p><p> In recent years, our country pay more and more attention to the integration of environmental monitoring network, integrated construction, crack down on fraud and environmental monitoring data, the industry will be pulled into the national regulatory perspective. Whether it is technology innovation, or monitoring points laid, debugging or environmental monitoring equipment upgrades, promote the mature process of environmental monitoring system in china.</p><p> Day ago, ecological environmental monitoring quality supervision and inspection of the three year action plan released, supervision to the people, to do, to single regulatory supervision, supervision, supervision to the data to segment the responsibility of great significance. According to the relevant responsible person said, the three year action plan aimed at the field of environmental monitoring focused on solving some contradictions, comprehensive coverage of monitoring mechanism, and operation mechanism of sewage units of three subjects. It can be said that this will be compacted layers of environmental responsibility, pollution behavior and effective measures of deterrence.</p><p> Environmental monitoring department official responded that three years of action will be in accordance with the &#34;double a randomized, open&#34; principle in 3 years to complete. By 2020, the basic realization of sound environmental monitoring data to ensure the quality of the responsibility system, effectively curb the behavior and the formation of &#34;data resort to deceit, dare not leave, do not want to leave, do not want to leave a good atmosphere&#34;. (source: China Environmental Network)</p><p><br/></p>', 291, 39, '');
