f Luanhe River<a href="https://wenwen.sogou.com/s/?w=%E5%9C%B0%E8%B4%A8%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0&ch=ww.xqy.chain" target="_self"> geological structure</a> Finally, repeated comparisons to determine the location of pier construction, and the bold decision to adopt the new method -- &#34;pneumatic caisson method&#34; to the pier.<a href="https://wenwen.sogou.com/s/?w=%E8%A9%B9%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%91&ch=ww.xqy.chain" target="_self"> Zhan Tianyou</a> As a success of Luan River Bridge built. This incident shocked the world: a China engineers had solved the problem of three foreign engineers can not complete.</p><p> Chuzhan victory after Zhan Tianyou, immediately encountered a more severe test. In 1905, the Qing government decided to build China&#39;s first railway<a href="https://wenwen.sogou.com/s/?w=%E4%BA%AC%E5%BC%A0%E9%93%81%E8%B7%AF&ch=ww.xqy.chain" target="_self"> The Beijing Zhangjiakou Railway</a> (Beijing to Zhangjiakou). Britain and Russia want to intervene, because of strong opposition Chinese people, they can not attempt to succeed. British envoy to Russia threatening: &#34;if Beijing Zhang railway engineer China built himself, that has nothing to do with Britain and russia.&#34; They thought that Chinese can not build this railway. At this critical moment,<a href="https://wenwen.sogou.com/s/?w=%E8%A9%B9%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%91&ch=ww.xqy.chain" target="_self"> Zhan Tianyou</a> Do not hesitate to take over this<a href="https://wenwen.sogou.com/s/?w=%E8%89%B0%E5%B7%A8%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1&ch=ww.xqy.chain" target="_self"> Arduous task</a> Responsible for building, Jing Zhang railway. The news came out, some of the imperialists and the British newspaper said wryly: &#34;not born to Chinese built the railroad engineers in the womb! Chinese does not want to rely on foreigners to repair their own railway, even if not a dream, at least fifty years.&#34; They even attacked Zhan Tianyou as head and chief engineer is &#34;proud as Lucifer&#34;, &#34;Too Big for Her Skin&#34;. Zhan Tianyou under pressure to appoint a foreign engineer, and said: &#34;in a way China vast territory and abundant resources, the industry must rely on outsiders, I think!&#34; &#34;China woke up, Chinese must use their own money to the engineer and railway construction.&#34;</p><p> August 1905, Beijing Zhangjiakou Railway officially started, intense exploration, the line began. Zhan Tianyou took the survey team, carrying instruments, day and night rush in the mountain. One evening, violent<a href="https://wenwen.sogou.com/s/?w=%E8%A5%BF%E5%8C%97%E9%A3%8E&ch=ww.xqy.chain" target="_self"> Northwest wind</a> Rolled in sand<a href="https://wenwen.sogou.com/s/?w=%E5%85%AB%E8%BE%BE%E5%B2%AD&ch=ww.xqy.chain" target="_self"> Badaling section of the Great Wall</a> Along the roaring and blew open her eyes, the survey team anxious to end, fill in a measured number, climb down from the wall.<a href="https://wenwen.sogou.com/s/?w=%E8%A9%B9%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%91&ch=ww.xqy.chain" target="_self"> Zhan Tianyou</a> Took the book, while looking to fill in the digital side, puzzled and asked: &#34;accurate data&#34;? &#34;Almost&#34;, measuring players answered. Zhan Tianyou said solemnly: &#34;the first is the technical requirements of precision, can not have a little vague and reckless,&#34; probably &#34;and&#34; almost &#34;this kind of argument should not be out of the mouth of the engineering staff.&#34; Then, he recited instruments, braving the wind, re struggling to climb to the rock, carefully review again, fixed an error. When he came down, lips<a href="https://wenwen.sogou.com/s/?w=%E5%86%BB%E9%9D%92&ch=ww.xqy.chain" target="_self"> Frozen green</a> The.</p><p> Soon, exploration and construction into the most difficult stage. In Badaling,<a href="https://wenwen.sogou.com/s/?w=%E9%9D%92%E9%BE%99%E6%A1%A5&ch=ww.xqy.chain" target="_self"> Qinglongqiao</a> Along the mountains overlap, steep cliffs, to the four tunnels, the longest over one thousand meters.<a href="https://wenwen.sogou