f="https://wenwen.sogou.com/s/?w=%E4%BA%AC%E5%BC%A0%E9%93%81%E8%B7%AF&ch=ww.xqy.chain" target="_self"> The Beijing Zhangjiakou Railway</a> Workers after several struggles, finally opened in September 1909. Six years to complete the original plan, the results of only four years ahead of schedule, cost only 1/5 of the valuation and foreigners. Some European engineers visit after tut praise, praise<a href="https://wenwen.sogou.com/s/?w=%E8%A9%B9%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%91&ch=ww.xqy.chain" target="_self"> Zhan Tianyou</a> Amazing。 But Zhan Tianyou has said modestly: &#34;this is the Beijing Zhangjiakou Railway more than 10000 staff strength, not my personal credit, the glory should belong to everyone.&#34;</p><p> Beijing Zhangjiakou Railway is completed, Zhan Tianyou succeeded<a href="https://wenwen.sogou.com/s/?w=%E7%B2%A4%E6%B1%89%E9%93%81%E8%B7%AF&ch=ww.xqy.chain" target="_self"> the Canton-Hankou railway</a> Supervisor and chief engineer. At this time, the United States decided to grant him a doctorate in engineering, he personally went to the United States in the investiture ceremony. In order to fully participate in railway construction of the motherland, he gave up this honor.</p><p> After the revolution of 1911,<a href="https://wenwen.sogou.com/s/?w=%E8%A9%B9%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%91&ch=ww.xqy.chain" target="_self"> Zhan Tianyou</a> In order to revitalize the railway business, and the establishment of a peer of the Chinese Academy of engineering, and pushed for the president. During this period, his training of young engineers devoted a lot of effort, he in addition to their own behavior to set an example, but also encouraged the young &#34;lapping academic, for invention&#34;, asking them &#34;not to Quji people, do not sell fishing known. Sincere things, not with small private,<a href="https://wenwen.sogou.com/s/?w=%E5%9C%AD%E7%92%A7&ch=ww.xqy.chain" target="_self"> high ethical standard</a><a href="https://wenwen.sogou.com/s/?w=%E6%9D%9F%E8%BA%AB&ch=ww.xqy.chain" target="_self"> Recoil</a> For example.&#34;</p><p>  <a href="https://wenwen.sogou.com/s/?w=%E8%A9%B9%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%91&ch=ww.xqy.chain" target="_self"> Zhan Tianyou</a> In the railway industry for thirty years, and was almost every railway in our country has different degree. In old age, due to overwork, unfortunately died in 1919.<a href="https://wenwen.sogou.com/s/?w=%E5%91%A8%E6%81%A9%E6%9D%A5&ch=ww.xqy.chain" target="_self"> Zhou Enlai</a> Comrade spoke highly of<a href="https://wenwen.sogou.com/s/?w=%E8%A9%B9%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%91&ch=ww.xqy.chain" target="_self"> Zhan Tianyou</a> The feat, said he was &#34;Chinese glory&#34;.</p><p><span style="font-size:29px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333"><br/></span></p><p> (2) Feng Kang</p><p><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180814/1534225059132363.jpg" title=" 1534225059132363.jpg" alt=" Feng Kang 2.jpg"/></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体"> 　</span> 　<strong> Study on topological groups and generalized function</strong></p><p> Before 1957, Feng Kang mainly engaged in basic mathematics study. His earliest work (not published) is to generate sub symplectic groups and four dimension<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=64570881&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> The fundamental theorem of algebra</a> Topological proof. Then he studied almost periodic topological group theory, this is 1934 by J.<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=29333&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Von Neumann</a> (von Neumann) and founder.<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=26225638&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> unitary matrix</a> Performance is closely linked. According to group all unitary expression levels between the two extreme types: unitary performance maximally almost periodic group -- &#34;enough&#34; minimum; almost periodic group without nontrivial unitary matrix representation. 1936 A.<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=64705026&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> weil</a> (Weil and H.)<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=387390&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Froden Starr</a> (Freudenthal) to solve the problem of very large characterization, they are compact groups and Euclidean vector group direct product. In 1940 von Neumann and E. Wigner (Wigner) for very small group has made great progress, but the problem has not been resolved. In 1950 Feng Kang took the lead on the linear Li (Lie) group (and covering group) to solve this problem: not necessary and sufficient conditions of ordinary unitary matrix is the performance of the &#34;nature&#34; can not be exchanged with non compact. This results in the later unitary representation theory and physical applications more show its importance.</p><p> In early 50s, L. Schwarz (Schwartz) is proposed<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=9755091&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Generalized function</a> System theory, attracted worldwide attention. Since 1954, the research of this field in Feng Kang, published the &#34;generalized function theory&#34; s comprehensive paper, also contains some new results, to promote the development of this theory in China. He also set up a discrete function of generalized function (function and its derivative) and continuous function between<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=70913001&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Duality theorem</a> . He should be professor Hua Luogeng&#39;s suggestion, a generalized Merlin<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=10665630&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Transform theory</a> For,<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=411661&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> partial differential equation</a> And the theory of analytic functions are applied abroad, late 60s similar work.</p><p><br/></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体"> 　</span> 　<strong> The founding of the finite element method</strong></p><p> At the end of 50s and early 60s, computational mathematics in China is just starting soon, in the case of foreign contact, Feng Kang led a team of scientific and technological personnel out from practice to theory, then<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=101154698&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> From theory to practice</a> The development of Chinese mathematics success. At the time of the study to solve the engineering design should be a large number of large elliptic equation analysis computation, has accumulated rich experience and effective. Feng Kang to sum up, make the theoretical results system. In 1965, Feng Kang in the &#34;Computational Mathematics&#34; published a paper &#34;variational principle based on differential format&#34;, is Chinese independent western system founded the finite element method mark.</p><p> This paper presents for all types of two order elliptic boundary value problems of the system<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=139767030&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Discretization method</a> . In order to ensure the flexibility of geometry, the regional Omega can be used for any appropriate section, the piecewise interpolation function accordingly, they form a Co.<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=817675&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Dimensional space</a> S is the solution of the original problem space is C. successfully.<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=83192569&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> sobolev</a> (c c c o PI has been generalized function space (H1) omega).<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=9025726&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Subspace</a> . Based on the variational principle, the equivalent to the original question in H1 (omega) on the positive two<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=8846913&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Function</a> The minimum problem into a minimization problem of finite dimensional subspace quadratic function on S, positive definite properties remain strictly. The discrete form is called so obtained based on the variational principle.<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=61368076&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Difference scheme</a> That is, the standard finite element method. This paper gives the stability theorem, discrete approximation theorem and convergence theorem, and reveals the advantages of this method in processing, boundary conditions, characteristic of flexible adaptability and reliable theory etc.. This is especially suitable for solving large complex problems, and easy to implement on computer.</p><p><br/></p><p> &#60;strong&#62; The natural boundary reduction and natural boundary element method&#60;/strong&#62;</p><p> Since 60s, the finite element method has achieved great success of elliptic boundary value problem for bounded domain solution, is widely used in engineering and scientific computing, is a major achievement in computational mathematics. But some actual calculation area computation problem is unbounded, with bounded region to approximate the unbounded domain, in order to achieve the required precision, the calculation will increase greatly, the boundary element method is an effective way to solve this problem.</p><p> On the boundary of the differential equation thought, as early as first Century had already appeared, but it is applied to numerical calculation of this century began in 60s, this is the boundary element method, the differential equation for domestication on the boundary integral equation.</p><p> Due to the different domestication method, numerical results of various boundary element methods are not the same. Feng Kang according to the physical characteristics of this kind of problem, reference<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=3308283&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Hadamard</a> (Hadamard) - type singular kernel, the concept of natural domestication, through natural domestication, energy is constant, so as to maintain the essence of the problem. In this concept, he proposed the natural boundary element method. The method of removing all the boundary element method for common advantages, but also have many unique features: the energy unchanged through natural domestication, the nature of the original elliptic boundary value problems are retained, thus ensuring the existence, uniqueness and stability of solutions of the natural integral equation, and that the nature and the finite element method direct coupling, thus forming a finite element and boundary element coupling fully inclusive and equitable and natural integrity system, flexibility to adapt to large complex problems, easy decomposition. This is the current decomposition method and parallel computation of correlation and the rise of regional pioneering work. As a special case of Feng Kang Helmholtz (Helmholtz) equation of cable of the classical ink and infinity<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=677336&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Rumsfeld</a> (Sommerfeld) radiation conditions corresponding to the integral type poor distant radiation conditions with theory and application value. Natural boundary element method advocated by Feng Kang by domestic and foreign experts known as one of the three schools on the international boundary element method, the direction has been by his students and other scholars in the continued development.</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p> &#60;strong&#62; Hamiltonian system Hamiltonian algorithm founded&#60;/strong&#62;</p><p> Classical mechanics has 3 equivalent mathematical formalism: Newton (Newton) system, Lagrange system (Lagrange) and Hamilton (Hamilton) system, the Hamilton system with symmetry has been outstanding, mathematical tools to research the theory of physics. All the real physical process of conservation can be expressed as the Hamiltonian system, whether it is classic,<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=10528142&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Quantum</a> Or relativistic, no matter<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=65662142&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> The number of degrees of freedom</a> For finite or infinite, always showed Harrington appropriate form. The mathematical basis of Haversian system is symplectic geometry. Symplectic geometry is the foundation of modern physics and mechanics, and it<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=305484&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> euclid geometry</a> The same plays an important role.</p><p> An important problem of Hamiltonian system is the stability problem, characteristic in geometry is its solution in<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=483263&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> phase space</a> Is the area preserving.<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=47811356&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> characteristic equation</a> The root is<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=8340524&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Pure imaginary</a> The. We can not use the asymptotic stability of the classical theory of them. For a long time, calculation method for Hamilton equation which has important physical significance of the world is almost blank. This situation with the Harrington system the universality and importance of contrast is very disproportionate.</p><p> Feng Kang published in International Conference on differential geometry and differential equations in a 1984 paper &#34;and the symplectic difference scheme&#34;, first put forward the Hamiltonian equations and Hamiltonian algorithm (i.e. symplectic geometry algorithm or symplectic geometry algorithm, format) are presented from symplectic geometry internal system and the nature of the way of research, put forward his unique insights on the whole issue, which opened up the field full of vitality and development prospects of the Hamiltonian algorithm, the computational mechanics and computational mathematics, computational physics of the combination of penetration of the front interface.</p><p><br/></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体"> 　</span> 　<strong> To Chinese science development mission</strong></p><p> Because in the early days of the war with Feng Kang<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=280201&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Bone tuberculosis</a> And because, in difficult circumstances out of medicine, so that the spine to his disability, life brings a lot of suffering and pain, but he hardtop over. Any contact with him or to work with people all are convinced by his motherland science tireless pursuit of spirit. He asks nothing of his own life, think, do is the cause of science. Even though he has already made the founding of the finite element method internationally recognized the significant achievements in 1965, but did not meet. His strong<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=7813934&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Enterprising</a> Prompted him to have been walking in the forefront of the world mathematics team.</p><p> Feng Kang learned, have deep knowledge in physics, mathematics, computer science and other fields. In science, he was always able to grasp the nature of things, the use of dialectical analysis, to find there are broad prospects for development in the theory and application of the subject, put forward original thoughts, basic skills and excellent application to solve specific difficulties, successfully open innovation direction, a new road open up a new field has important practical significance, and led a group of a group of people to make outstanding contributions in a new direction.</p><p> In scientific research, he advocated<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=370051&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Theory and Practice</a> And rigorous attitude toward science. He has theoretical questions for a calculation method of strict in demands, each proposed are tested in the actual calculation, for the calculation method of good test is to promote the use of, make it into productive forces, for the construction of modernization services. Not only he himself personally, but also for the scientific research personnel is required.</p><p><br/></p>', 443, 104, '');
