refers to the craftsmen not only has superb skills and superb skills, but also have \r\n rigorous, meticulous, dedicated and responsible attitude and clear, improving work concept, as well as the occupation identity, sense of responsibility, sense of honor and mission.</pre><pre> In fact,, artisan spirit has the different view in each country, the Germans called &#34;labor spirit&#34;, the Americans called &#34;occupation spirit&#34;, Japanese called &#34;artisan spirit&#34;, Koreans call &#34;Master spirit&#34;.</pre><pre> By Germany and Japan and other countries a comparative study of the artisan spirit prevailed, and on China&#39;s ancient craftsman spirit collection, great artisan spirit is mainly embodied in the following five aspects: persistent attention, rigorous style, excellence, dedication and trustworthiness, innovation.</pre><pre> Persistent attention</pre><pre> We found, either Germany or Japan,</pre><pre> In world manufacturing stage, &#34;made in Germany&#34; has held high. At present, in the 31 sector of the global manufacturing industry in Germany, 17 occupy a leading position in the top 3 departments a total of 27. \r\n German cars, watches, knives, brewing equipment, underground drainage system, building and furniture, are known to feature durable, reliable, safe and precision etc.. This also constitutes the core of &#34;culture made in Germany&#34;.</pre><p><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;"> December 14, 2016,<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/v75853589.htm" target="_self"> Specification language</a> Journals &#34;<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/v64340288.htm" target="_self"> Ruminate upon a subject</a> &#34;Announced<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/v158035210.htm" target="_self"> In 2016 ten pandemic</a> , &#34;artisan spirit&#34; selected.<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/v158038951.htm?fromTitle=%E5%B7%A5%E5%8C%A0%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E#quote1"> [1]</a></p><p style="text-align:center"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><a href="https://baike.sogou.com/PicBooklet.v?relateImageGroupIds=&lemmaId=158038951&now=https://pic.baike.soso.com/ugc/baikepic2/14838/20180127172457-562888478_jpg_534_300_112284.jpg/0&type=1" title=""><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180725/1532515192693562.jpg" title=" 1532515192693562.jpg" alt=" 13.jpg"/></a></span></p><p style="text-indent: 32px;line-height: 24px;background: white"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#333333"> Artisan spirit (2016 government work report of new words) artisan spirit refers to the craft workers on products crafted, the pursuit of the ultimate concept, each process of production, for excellence in every detail, and strive to perfect products.</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 15px;text-indent: 32px;line-height: 24px;background: white"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#333333"> Two thousand and sixteen</span><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#333333"> The year of March 5th,</span><a href="https://baike.sogou.com/v148544638.htm" target="_self"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#333333"> Li Keqiang</span></a><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#333333"> The prime minister &#34;</span><a href="https://baike.sogou.com/v481973.htm" target="_self"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#333333"> The government work report</span></a><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#333333"> &#34;Said, to encourage enterprises to carry out</span><a href="https://baike.sogou.com/v70802487.htm" target="_self"><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#333333"> Customization</span></a><span style="font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#333333"> And flexible production, cultivate excellence artisan spirit&#34;. Artisan spirit &#34;quickly became popular, has become a hot word in manufacturing industry. Then, not only the manufacturing industry, all walks of life advocate artisan spirit&#34;. Thus, the use of range expansion, any industry, any person &#34;excellence, and strive to perfect&#34; the spirit, can be called &#34;artisan spirit&#34;.</span></p><p style="background: white"><span style="font-size:32px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#333333"> (2) definition</span></p><p> The reason why the column fourth is a dedicated and trustworthy country because artisan spirit, dedication and integrity are two important aspects of the socialist core value concept in china.<br/> <br/> Devotion is the dedication. That is love their jobs, respect their duties, devote to career; not only to his work as an occupation, it is more important as a career, dry line, love line. Because, &#34;learning is good, good as music, only the love of their industry, and professional positions, to be able to devote themselves into the work, in order to dry out the results, become a&#34; great artisan&#34;. In practical work, dedication is down-to-earth, working hard, excluding gains and losses, doing their own hard work; it is indifferent to fame and wealth, dedication, insist Aoyama do not relax. We often say that the hard-working, unknown to the public, strict in demands and improving, make painstaking efforts, dedicated, diligently, be tireless in teaching others, are the best refinement of professionalism.<br/> Is honest and trustworthy. That is what abide by the occupation morals, prestige, not resort to deceit.</p><h1 style="margin-top:0;margin-right:10px;margin-bottom:0;margin-left: 0;margin-bottom:0;line-height:34px;background:white"><span style="font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:#333333"> Modern figure case</span></h1><h1> (1) Gao Fenglin</h1><h1 style="margin-top:0;margin-right:10px;margin-bottom:0;margin-left: 0;margin-bottom:0;line-height:34px;background:white"><span style="font-size:30px;font-family:宋体;color:#333333;font-weight:normal"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180814/1534225109930544.jpg" title=" 1534225109930544.jpg" alt=" Gao Fenglin 1.jpg"/></span></h1><h1 style="margin-top:0;margin-right:10px;margin-bottom:0;margin-left: 0;margin-bottom:0;line-height:34px;background:white"><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:宋体;font-weight:normal"> A contribution</span></h1><p> LM-2E rocket in the development of production, the arrow vibration test of the tower 80 meters up to the &#34;key LM-2E&#34; in development, and the tower is used to weld the supporting beam of rocket vibration is the key key, the requirements of special materials, a weld. Gao Fenglin after repeated test, put forward the multilevel fast continuous welding and mechanical thermal conductivity and a series of methods of ensuring the performance of the process, to complete the outstanding vibration beam welding research, to ensure the timely completion of the tower vibration and LM-2E rocket scheduled test, to ensure the successful launch of the star of Australia, engineering research projects of the first prize. The day before, in<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=6464651&ss_c=ssc.citiao.link" target="_self"> Manned space engineering</a> Upgrade test vibration beam welding quality is still good, bearing capacity increased from 360 tons to 420 tons, safe and sound beam. 　</p><p> For new large thrust engine, long three, three long triacetate C rocket design, due to the use of new materials and new technology brings many problems for the welding process, especially in large and small end engine nozzle welding, butt welding, super thick and thin material in the complex structure of the many leaks, Gao Fenglin after repeated analysis and exploration, to finally find out<a href="https://baike.sogou.com/lemma/ShowInnerLink.htm?lemmaId=64504179&ss_c=