INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(126, '首页->继续前行->精神永流传->改革精神->改革精神', 'Home Page->Future->The spirit is forever->The spirit of reform->The spirit of reform', '1532517392', '2018-08-29', '00:10:27', '1', '<p style="text-align:center"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180828/1535470433288705.jpg" title="1535470433288705.jpg" alt="gaigekaifang1.jpg"/></span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">邓小平与改革开放：发展是硬道理，发展中国特色社会主义是发展中国的硬道理。在全面深化改革时期，邓小平对党和人民卓越的历史性贡献，为中国特色社会主义的发展提供了极为重要的思想资源。</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">改革开放的精神：1、解放和发展社会生产力。2、提高综合国力。3、进一步解放人民思想,建设有中国特色的社会主义。<br/> 改革开放意义：为尽快提升经济发展速度，邓小平与党内的开明派(改革八贤等)开始逐一解决这些问题，并试图改变人民心目中对共产党和社会主义根深蒂固的形象，这场改革运动的目的是以维持社会主义制度为前提，改变生产中不适应生产发展的管理体制和政策，并建立社会主义下的市场经济体制。这场改革的经济方面在农村取得了率先突破，并随之迅速在全国各经济领域内推行改革。<br/> 改革开放内容：<br/> 改革开放是邓小平理论的重要组成部分，中国社会主义建设的一项根本方针。改革，包括经济体制改革，即把高度集中的计划经济体制改革成为社会主义市场经济体制；政治体制改革，包括发展民主，加强法制，实现政企分开、精简机构，完善民主监督制度，维护安定团结。开放，主要指对外开放，在广泛意义上还包括对内开放。改革开放是中国共产党在社会主义初级阶段基本路线的基本点之一，是中国走向富强的必经之路。对中国的经济发展有着巨大影响。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180828/1535470497370973.jpg" title="1535470497370973.jpg"/></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180828/1535470498139887.jpg" title="1535470498139887.jpg"/></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">郑培民：原籍河北省武安市，1943年7月23日出生于吉林省海龙县海龙镇一个普通工人家庭。<br/></span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">1950年至1962年就读于海龙县城关小学和第四、第五中学。 </span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">1962年9月以优异成绩考入吉林大学物理系学习，担任系学生会主席。</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">1968年7月至1970年3月，到辽宁省3275部队锻炼。</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">1970年3月分配到湖南省湘潭电机厂工作，先后担任厂革委会组织组干事、厂子弟中学党支部书记、厂团委副书记、厂党委办主任、厂党委副书记兼纪委书记。</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">其间，1981年2月至1982年8月在清华大学经济管理工程系经济管理研究班学习。他以党的事业为重，心系企业，为企业党的建设和企业发展做了大量卓有成效的工作，深受广大干部职工的尊敬和爱戴。</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">1983年6月至1992年10月，郑培民先后担任湘潭市委副书记、书记，湘西土家族苗族自治州委书记。在市、州工作的近10年里，他兢兢业业，夙兴夜寐，访贫问苦，体察民情，带领广大干部群众大力推进改革，发展经济，促进了湘潭市和自治州的两个文明建设。</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">1992年10月至1995年10月，郑培民担任湖南省人民政府副省长。他在分管教育工作时，注重调查研究，坚决贯彻执行党的教育方针，为全省教育事业的发展做出了突出贡献。分管农业和农村工作时，围绕省委、省政府提出的战略目标，在发展优质高产高效农业、防汛救灾、水利建设、扶贫、减轻农民负担等方面，做出了显著成绩。</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">1995年10月，郑培民担任省委副书记后，勇于改革创新，为湖南广播电视、出版、体育事业的发展和促进全省党的思想、组织、作风建设做出了重要贡献。</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">2001年1月，郑培民当选为省人大常委会副主任，同年11月起主持省人大常委会工作。他坚持以经济立法为重点，加强地方法规建设，注重发挥监督职能作用，为推进依法治省做出了新的成绩。</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">2002年3月11日，因突发心肌梗塞，在北京逝世，享年59岁。</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">       改革是推动新时代中国特色社会主义实践的强大动力。改革既是破解发展难题的治本之策,也是社会主义制度的自我完善和发展,是充分发挥中国特色社会主义制度优势的有力手段。完善和发展中国特色社会主义制度,推进国家治理体系和治理能力现代化,是全面深化改革的总目标,也是新时代坚持和发展中国特色社会主义基本方略的重要组成部分。这一目标超越了现代政治学和行政学的“治理”概念,体现了以习近平同志为核心的党中央的政治智慧和勇气。</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">       不忘初心、牢记使命,把改革开放伟大事业不断推向前进,需要我们在新时代继续弘扬“红船精神”和“改革精神”,把人民对美好生活的向往作为全面深化改革的方向,坚定不移推进改革,努力在全面建成小康社会和社会主义现代化强国建设新征程中,取得新的辉煌成就。（来源：光明网）</span><br/></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"> </span></p><p><br/></p>', '<p style="text-align:center"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: white;"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180828/1535470433288705.jpg" title=" 1535470433288705.jpg" alt=" Gaigekaifang1.jpg"/></span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"> Deng Xiaoping: the reform and opening up and the development is the hard truth, the development of socialism China characteristics is the development of the hard truth China. In the comprehensive deepening reform period, Deng Xiaoping history of the party and the people&#39;s outstanding contributions for the development of socialism, Chinese provides important ideological resources.</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"> The spirit of reform and opening up: 1, the liberation and development of productive forces. 2, enhance the comprehensive national strength. 3, further emancipate the minds of the people, building a socialist Chinese.<br/> The significance of the reform and opening up: to enhance the speed of economic development as soon as possible, Deng Xiaoping and the Liberal Party (eight Xian reform etc.) began to solve these problems, and try to change the image of the Communist Party and the socialist ingrained in the minds of the people, the reform movement is the premise to maintain the socialist system, change the development of production management system and the policy does not meet the production, and the establishment of socialist market economic system. The economic aspect of the reform has made the first breakthrough in the countryside, and then quickly in the whole nation each economic field reform.<br/> The contents of the reform and opening up:<br/> The reform and opening up is an important part of Deng Xiaoping theory, a fundamental principle of socialist construction China. The reform, including the reform of the economic system, which is a highly centralized planned economy system reform has become a socialist market economic system; reform of the political system, including the development of democracy, strengthen the legal system, realizing the separation of government and enterprise, streamline the organization and improve the system of democratic supervision, maintain stability and unity. Open, mainly refers to the opening, is also included in the broad sense of opening up. The reform and opening up is one of the basic points of China basic line in the primary stage of socialism, is the only way which must be passed China towards prosperity. Have a huge impact on the economic development of China.</span></p><p><br/></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180828/1535470497370973.jpg" title=" 1535470497370973.jpg"/></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><img src="/chuxin/ueditor/php/upload/image/20180828/1535470498139887.jpg" title=" 1535470498139887.jpg"/></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"> Zheng Peimin: from Hebei city of Wuan Province, was born in July 23, 1943 in dragon dragon county of Jilin Province town of an ordinary worker&#39;s family.<br/></span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"> From 1950 to 1962 at the county primary school and the Dragon fourth, Fifth Middle school.</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"> September 1962 with honors admitted to the Department of physics of Jilin University, served as chairman of student union.</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"> From July 1968 to March 1970, to the Liaoning province 3275 military exercise.</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"> March 1970 assigned to the Hunan province Xiangtan motor factory factory, has served as the Revolutionary Committee Organization group director, branch secretary, deputy party secretary, factory high school league factory factory Party committee office director, factory deputy secretary and Secretary of the party committee.</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"> During the February 1981 to August 1982 study at Tsinghua University Department of economic management engineering management of economy class. He loves the company to the party&#39;s cause, and do a lot of work for the very fruitful enterprise party construction and enterprise development, the majority of cadres and workers of the respect and love.</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"> From June 1983 to October 1992, Zheng Peimin served as Deputy Secretary of Xiangtan Municipal Committee, Xiangxi Tujia and Miao Autonomous zhouweishuji. In the city, work in the past 10 years, he dedicated, compassionate, hard at work night and day, visit the poor and the suffering, leading cadres and the masses to vigorously promote the reform and development of economy, promoting the civilization construction of Xiangtan city and autonomous prefecture, two.</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"> From October 1992 to October 1995, Zheng Peimin served as vice governor of Hunan Provincial People&#39;s government. He was in charge of education, pay attention to investigation and study, and resolutely implement the party&#39;s education policy, made outstanding contributions to the development of the province&#39;s education. In charge of agriculture and rural work, around the strategic goal of the provincial Party committee and government, in the development of high quality and high efficiency in agriculture, water conservancy, flood control and disaster relief, poverty alleviation, reduce farmer burden etc., made significant achievements.</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"> In October 1995, Zheng Peimin served as Deputy Secretary of the provincial Party committee, the courage to reform and innovation, has made an important contribution to the Hunan radio and television, publishing, sports development, and promote the construction of ideology, organization, style of the party.</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"> In January 2001, Zheng Peimin was elected vice chairman of the NPC Standing Committee, in November the same year the provincial people&#39;s Congress Standing Committee presided over the work. He insisted on the economic legislation as the focus, strengthen the construction of local laws and regulations, pay attention to the supervision function, make new achievements for the province to promote the rule of law.</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"> In March 11, 2002, due to a sudden myocardial infarction, died in Beijing at the age of 59.</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"> Reform is to promote the new era of strong power of socialist practice China characteristics. Fundamental reform is the problem of crack development, self-improvement and development of socialist system, is a powerful means to give full play to the advantages of the socialist system China characteristics. The improvement and development of Chinese socialist system, promote national governance systems and governance capacity modernization, is the overall goal of deepening the reform, but also an important part of the new era and adhere to the basic strategy of socialism development China characteristics. This goal beyond the modern political science and administrative science reflects the concept of &#34;governance&#34;, with Comrade Xi Jinping as the core of the CPC Central Committee&#39;s political wisdom and courage.</span></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"> Not forget the early heart, remember our mission, to continuously push forward the great cause of reform and opening up, we need to continue to carry forward the &#34;red boat&#34; spirit and the spirit of reform in the new era, the people yearning for a better life as the direction of deepening the reform, and unswervingly push forward the reform efforts in the construction of a comprehensive well-off the society and socialist modernization in the new journey, the brilliant achievements of the new. (source: Guangming)</span><br/></p><p style="line-height: 3em;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">  </span></p><p><br/></p>', 451, 69, '');
