INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(171, '1947-06月底 三路大军打到外线去', '1947-06 the end of the month three army to go outside', '1534029204', '2018-08-12', '07:16:00', 'del', '<p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">三路大军打到外线去</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">/</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">人民解放战争的战略进攻的序幕由此揭开。</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体">三路大军挺进中原战役是</span>1947<span style="font-family:宋体">年（民国三十六年）</span>6<span style="font-family:宋体">月至</span>12<span style="font-family:宋体">月，在第三次国内革命战争中，人民解放军晋冀鲁豫野战军与华东野战军主力强渡黄河，进击中原国民党军的战略性进攻行动。</span></p><p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"></span><br/></p>', '<p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> Three army to go outside</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;"> /</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> A prelude to the strategic offensive of the people&#39;s Liberation War which opened the.</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体"> Three army into the Central Plains campaign</span> One thousand nine hundred and forty-seven<span style="font-family:宋体"> (in thirty-six years)</span> Six<span style="font-family:宋体"> January</span> Twelve<span style="font-family:宋体"> In August, during the third revolutionary civil war, the people&#39;s Liberation Army Shanxi field army and the main force of the Yellow River East China Field Army, the Central Plains on the Kuomintang army strategic offensive action.</span></p><p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"></span><br/></p>', 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(172, '1947-09~13 中国共产党在河北省石家庄市西柏坡村举行全国土地会议通过《中国土地大法大纲》', '1947-09~13 Chinese Communist Party in Xibaipo village in Hebei Province, Shijiazhuang city held a national land conference through &#34;Chinese land law outline&#34;', '1534029444', '2018-08-29', '23:56:38', '2', '<p>《中国土地法大纲》于1947年9月13日由中国共产党在河北省石家庄市西柏坡村举行全国土地会议通过，同年10月10日由中共中央公布施行。规定废除封建剥削土地制度，实行耕者有其田。没收地主的土地财产，征收富农多余的土地财产；废除一切祠堂、庙宇、寺院、学校、机关团体的土地所有权和乡村在土地改革以前的一切债务；以乡或村为单位统一分配土地，数量上抽多补少，质量上抽肥补瘦，所有权归农户所有。 土改前的土地契约、债约一律缴销；工商业者的财产及其他营业受法律保护，不受侵犯。本法公布前已平均分配的地区，农民不要求重分，可不重分。它的公布与实行总结了中国共产党二十多年土地革命基本经验教训，是一个正确的土地纲领，体现了土地改革的总路线。</p>', '<p> The &#34;Outline&#34; the law of the land China in September 13, 1947 by the Communist Party Chinese in Xibaipo village in Hebei Province, Shijiazhuang city held a national land conference by October 10th of the same year, published by the CPC Central Committee implementation. Provisions of the abolition of the feudal system of land exploitation, the implementation of land to the tiller. Land confiscation of property expropriation, peasants surplus land property; the abolition of all ancestral temples, monasteries, schools, government agencies and organizations of the rural land ownership and all debts in the land reform before; the township or village as a unit of unified allocation of land, the number of pumping less, the quality of choufeibushou, ownership all the farmers. Before the land reform, land contract, debt cancellation will be about; industrial and commercial property and other business shall be protected by law, are not violated. Before the promulgation of this law has the average distribution area, farmers do not require heavy, not heavy points. It is promulgated and implemented more than 20 years of Communist Party Chinese summarizes the basic experience of the agrarian revolution is a lesson, correct land program, reflecting the general line of land reform.</p>', 296, 32, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(173, '1948-04-30 五一口号', '1948-04-30 51 slogan', '1534029497', '2018-08-12', '07:18:17', 'del', '<p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">五一口号，这是我国统一战线和多党合作发展史上一件具有里程碑意义的事件，标志着各民主党派和无党派人士公开、自觉地接受了中国共产党的领导，标志着各民主党派和无党派人士坚定地走上了新民主主义、社会主义的道路，标志着中国的民主政治建设和政党制度建设揭开了新的一页。</span></p>', '<p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> 51 slogan, this is a milepost event in the united front of China and the history of the development of a multi-party cooperation, marking the democratic parties and non party personages openly and consciously accept the leadership of the Communist Party of China, marking the democratic parties and non party personages firmly on the new democratic socialist road. Marks of democratic political construction and political system construction of the Chinese has opened a new page.</span></p>', 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(174, '1948-09-~1949-02 辽沈、淮海、平津战役', '1948-09-~1949-02 Liaoshen, Huaihai, Tianjin campaign', '1534029689', '2018-08-12', '07:21:29', 'del', '<p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">三大战役是指</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">1948</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">年</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">9</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">月至</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">1949</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">年</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">1</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">月，中国人民解放军同中华民国国军进行的战略决战，包括辽沈战役、淮海战役、平津战役三个战略性战役。辽沈、淮海、平津三大战役，历时</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">142</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">天，共争取起义、投诚、接受和平改编与歼灭国民党正规军</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">144</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">个师，非正规军</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">29</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">个师，合计共</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">154</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">万余人。国民党赖以维持其反动统治的主要军事力量基本上被消灭。三大战役的胜利，奠定了人民解放战争在全国胜利的基础。</span></p>', '<p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> The three refers to the battle</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;"> One thousand nine hundred and forty-eight</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> year</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;"> Nine</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> January</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;"> One thousand nine hundred and forty-nine</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> year</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;"> One</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> In June, the people&#39;s Liberation Army Chinese strategic battle for the Republic of China army, including the Liaoshen campaign, Huaihai Campaign and Pingjin battle three strategic battle. Liaoshen, Huaihai, Tianjin battle of the three, duration</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;"> One hundred and forty-two</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> Day, for a total uprising, to surrender, to accept the peace adaptation and annihilated the KMT army</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;"> One hundred and forty-four</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> A normal, non regular army</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;"> Twenty-nine</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> A teacher, a total of</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;"> One hundred and fifty-four</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> Million people. The Kuomintang&#39;s main military force to maintain its reactionary rule basically eliminated. The three big battle, laid the foundation of the people&#39;s Liberation War victory in the country.</span></p>', 0, 0, '');
