INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(177, '1949-03 河北，中共七届二中全会', '1949-03 Hebei, the Communist Party of China in the second Plenary Session of the 7th CPC Central Committee', '1534029994', '2018-08-12', '07:26:34', 'del', '<p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">河北，中共七届二中全。会</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;"></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">毛泽东同志在党的七届二中全会上提出的，要求全党在胜利面前要保持清醒头脑，在夺取全国政权后要经受住执政的考验，务必使同志们继续地保持谦虚、谨慎、不骄、不躁的作风，务必使同志们继续地保持艰苦奋斗的作风。</span></p>', '<p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> Hebei, the seven session of the second full. Meeting</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;"></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> Comrade Mao Zedong put forward in the party on the second Plenary Session of the 7th CPC Central Committee, asked the party to keep a clear mind in the face of success, to withstand the test of ruling after seizing state power, make sure the Comrades to remain modest, prudent and free from arrogance and rashness, Comrades make sure to maintain the style of hard struggle.</span></p>', 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(178, '1949-04-21 《向全国进军的命令》', '&#34;1949-04-21&#34; command to enter the country', '1534030056', '2018-08-12', '07:27:36', 'del', '<p><span style="font-family:宋体">毛泽东、朱德发布《向全国进军的命令》，于</span>23<span style="font-family:宋体">日占领南京，宣告延续</span>22<span style="font-family:宋体">年的国民党反动统治的覆灭</span></p><p><br/></p>', '<p><span style="font-family:宋体"> Mao Zedong, &#34;Zhu De issued an order to enter the country&#34;, in</span> Twenty-three<span style="font-family:宋体"> Japanese occupation of Nanjing, announced the continuation of</span> Twenty-two<span style="font-family:宋体"> The collapse of the Kuomintang&#39;s reactionary rule</span></p><p><br/></p>', 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(179, '1949-06-30 毛泽东发表《论人民民主专政》', '1949-06-30 Mao Zedong published &#34;on the people&#39;s democratic dictatorship&#34;', '1534030174', '2018-08-12', '07:29:34', 'del', '<p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">在中国新民主主义革命取得了决定性的胜利﹐全国性政权即将建立的时刻﹐</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">1949</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">年</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">6</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">月</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">30</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">日，毛泽东为纪念中国共产党成立二十八周年而写的一篇论文。根据马克思主义国家学说，结合中国实际，论述了即将成立的中华人民共和国的国家性质，各阶级在国家中的地位及其相互关系，国家对内、对外政策等。</span></p>', '<p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> Chinese won a decisive victory in the new democratic revolution, the regime will establish the moment,</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;"> One thousand nine hundred and forty-nine</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> year</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;"> Six</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> month</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;"> Thirty</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> Day, Mao Zedong to commemorate the founding of the Communist Party of Chinese 28th anniversary and a paper to write. According to Marx&#39;s theory of the state, combined with the actual Chinese, discusses the nature of the state to be set up in People&#39;s Republic of China, position of each class in the country and the relationship between the state of internal and external policies.</span></p>', 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(180, '1949-09-21~30 中国人民政治协商会议第一届全体会议北平中南海召开', 'The first plenary session of the 1949-09-21~30 China people&#39;s Political Consultative Conference held in Zhongnanhai, Beijing', '1534030585', '2018-08-27', '22:55:47', '2', '<p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"></span>1949年9月21日，中国人民政治协商会议第一届全体会议在北平中南海怀仁堂隆重开幕。毛泽东发表《中国人民站起来了》的著名讲话。会议选出了由毛泽东任主席的政协全国委员会。选举毛泽东为中央人民政府主席。会议通过了北平为中华人民共和国首都，将北平改名为北京。会议决定采用公元纪年。大会还通过了《中国人民政治协商会议共同纲领》，明确规定了中华人民共和国的国体和政体及内外政策<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"><br/></span></p>', '<p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"></span> In September 21, 1949, the first plenary session of Chinese people&#39;s Political Consultative Conference opened in Peking Zhongnanhai Huairen. Mao Zedong made a famous speech &#34;China people stand up.&#34;. The meeting elected CPPCC National committee chaired by the president Mao Zedong. Mao Zedong was elected chairman of the Central People&#39;s government. The meeting adopted the Beijing as the capital of People&#39;s Republic of China, Beijing will be renamed Beijing. The meeting decided to adopt the Gregorian calendar. Congress also passed the &#34;China people&#39;s Political Consultative Conference common program&#34;, defined the People&#39;s Republic of China state and political system and policies<span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"><br/></span></p>', 191, 104, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(181, '1949-10-01 中华人民共和国中央人民政府成立', '1949-10-01 People&#39;s Republic of China, the Central People&#39;s government set up', '1534030648', '2018-08-27', '22:45:08', '2', '<p>中华人民共和国中央人民政府成立/中华人民共和国成立后，中国共产党成为全国范围的执政党。</p><p>开国大典，是指1949年10月1日15：00在北京为中华人民共和国中央人民政府成立而举行的仪式，直到21：00才结束，是中华人民共和国成立的标志。</p><p>中华人民共和国的成立开辟了中国历史新纪元。从此，中国结束了一百多年来被侵略、被奴役的屈辱历史，真正成为独立自主的国家。</p><p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"></span><br/></p>', '<p> People&#39;s Republic of China Central People&#39;s government set up after the founding of the Communist Party of People&#39;s Republic of China, Chinese to become the ruling party.</p><p> Refers to the founding ceremony, 15:00 on October 1, 1949 in Beijing for the People&#39;s Republic of China Central People&#39;s government set up the ceremony, until 21:00 until the end, is a sign of the establishment of the People&#39;s Republic of China.</p><p> The establishment of the People&#39;s Republic of China opened a new era in the history Chinese. From then on, China ended more than 100 years of humiliation was invaded, enslaved, and truly become an independent country.</p><p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"></span><br/></p>', 276, 71, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(182, '1949-10-02 中国和苏联建交。', '1949-10-02 China and Soviet diplomatic relations.', '1534785209', '2018-08-27', '22:55:39', '2', '<p>中国和苏联建交。苏是第一个承认并与新中国建交的国家。</p>', '<p> Chinese and Soviet diplomatic relations. The Soviet Union was the first to recognize and establish diplomatic relations with new Chinese countries.</p>', 277, 100, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(183, '1950-02 新中国与外国签订的第一个条约。', 'The first treaty signed with foreign 1950-02 Chinese.', '1534785313', '2018-08-27', '22:55:29', '2', '<p>中国和苏联两国政府在莫斯科签署中苏友好同盟互助条约。毛泽东主席和苏联部长会议主席斯大林出席签字仪式。周恩来总理兼外长代表中国政府在条约上签字。这是新中国与外国签订的第一个条约。</p>', '<p> Chinese and Soviet governments signed the Sino Soviet Treaty of mutual friendship and alliance in moscow. President Mao Zedong and chairman of the Soviet Union ministers Stalin attended the signing ceremony. The prime minister and foreign minister Zhou Enlai signed the Treaty on behalf of the government China. This is the first signing of the Treaty of new Chinese with foreign countries.</p>', 326, 85, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(184, '1950-5 印度首任驻华大使潘尼迦向毛泽东主席递交国书。', '1950-5 India&#39;s first ambassador in China presented his credentials to President Mao Zedong pan child.', '1534785369', '2018-08-21', '01:16:09', 'del', '<p><span style="font-family:宋体">印度首任驻华大使潘尼迦向毛泽东主席递交国书。印是当时非社会主义国家中第一个与新中国建交的国家。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '<p><span style="font-family:宋体"> The first ambassador to the ambassador of India pan Ni Jia presented his credentials to President Mao Zedong. India is one of the first countries to establish diplomatic relations with the new China non socialist countries at that time.</span></p><p><br/></p>', 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(185, '1950-6 瑞典首任驻华大使阿马斯顿向毛泽东主席递交国书后宾主交谈。', 'The first 1950-6 Swedish ambassador A Marsden presented his credentials to President Mao Zedong after the conversation.', '1534785415', '2018-08-21', '01:16:55', 'del', '<p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">瑞典首任驻华大使阿马斯顿向毛泽东主席递交国书后宾主交谈。瑞系西方第一个与新中国建交的国家。</span></p>', '<p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> Sweden&#39;s first ambassador A Marsden presented his credentials to President Mao Zedong after the conversation. Rui Department of the first western countries to establish diplomatic relations with new China.</span></p>', 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(186, '1950-6-25 朝鲜内战爆发', 'The outbreak of the Korean civil war 1950-6-25', '1534785460', '2018-08-21', '01:17:40', 'del', '<p><span style="font-family:宋体">美国对朝鲜进行大规模军事干涉，并派兵侵占中国领土台湾，直接威胁中国安全。中国遂决定应朝方要求派志愿军入朝参战，抗美援朝，保家卫国</span>,<span style="font-family:宋体">在军事和外交两条战线同美国进行面对面的较量</span>,<span style="font-family:宋体">终于迫使美国不得不于</span>1953-7-27-<span style="font-family:宋体">签署朝鲜停战协定。</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体">抗美援朝和援越抗法斗争的胜利表明，新中国已成为维护亚洲和世界和平的一支重要力量。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '<p><span style="font-family:宋体"> The United States conducted a large-scale military intervention in North Korea, and sent troops to occupy China territory of Taiwan, a direct threat to the safety China. Chinese decided North Korea&#39;s request sent volunteers of the Korean War, the Korean War, protect our homes and defend our country</span> ,<span style="font-family:宋体"> In two military and diplomatic fronts with the United States face</span> ,<span style="font-family:宋体"> Finally forced the United States to</span> 1953-7-27-<span style="font-family:宋体"> The signing of the Korean Armistice agreement.</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体"> The Korean War and the Vietnam war against France victory shows that the new Chinese has become an important force to safeguard Asian and world peace.</span></p><p><br/></p>', 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(187, '1952 新中国第一次参加的奥运会', '1952 new Chinese first time to participate in the Olympic Games', '1534785585', '2018-08-27', '22:43:33', '2', '<p>新中国第一次参加的奥运会是1952年在芬兰赫尔辛基举办的第十五届奥运会。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> The new China first participated in the Olympic Games is held in Finland in 1952 fifteenth Helsinki Olympic games.</p><p><br/></p>', 266, 103, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(188, '1953-10-27 我国第一根无缝钢管在鞍钢无缝钢管厂压制成功。', '1953-10-27 China&#39;s first seamless steel tube successfully suppressed in Angang seamless steel pipe plant.', '1534785635', '2018-08-27', '17:51:21', '2', '<p>1953年10月27日，我国第一根无缝钢管在鞍钢无缝钢管厂压制成功。无缝钢管是航天、地质、石油、机械等工业行业必须的基础材料，能够生产无缝钢管，标志着我国向工业化迈进了一大步。</p>', '<p> In October 27, 1953, China&#39;s first successful suppression of seamless steel tube in Angang seamless steel tube plant. Seamless steel tube is a basic material for aerospace, geology, petroleum, machinery and other industries must, to the production of seamless steel pipe, China marks a major step forward to industrialization.</p>', 183, 71, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(189, '1953-12 周恩来总理首次提出了和平共处五项原则。', '1953-12 Prime Minister Zhou Enlai first proposed the five principles of peaceful coexistence.', '1534785695', '2018-08-27', '17:50:45', '2', '<p>中国和印度开始就中印关于中国西藏与印度之间的通商和交通协定进行谈判。周恩来总理首次提出了和平共处五项原则。经双方同意，五项原则被载入了该协定。</p>', '<p> Chinese and India began talks between Tibet and India China India on Trade and transport agreement. Premier Zhou Enlai first proposed the five principles of peaceful coexistence. With the consent of both parties, the five principles were included in the agreement.</p>', 344, 95, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(190, '1954-4~7 新中国首次作为五大国之一参加的重要国际会议', 'The new 1954-4~7 China for the first time as an important international conference to participate in one of the five powers', '1534785759', '2018-08-27', '17:50:33', '2', '<p>周恩来总理兼外长率中国代表团出席旨在和平解决朝鲜问题与恢复印度支那和平问题的-内瓦会议。这是新中国首次作为五大国之一参加的重要国际会议。周恩来总理兼外长率团与会，并以原则坚定、策略灵活的高超外交艺术，同其他与会国一道，排除了美国的干挠，为上述问题的解决发挥了重要作用。</p>', '<p> The prime minister and foreign minister Zhou Enlai rate delegation to North Korea Chinese to solve the problem of peace and restoration of peace in Indochina - the Geneva conference. This is a new Chinese for the first time as an important international conference to participate in one of the five powers. The prime minister and foreign minister Zhou Enlai led a delegation to attend the meeting, and to the firm principle and flexible strategies the superb art of diplomacy, with other participating States and ruled out the interference of the United States, has played an important role in solving these problems.</p>', 199, 68, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(191, '1954-07 新中国第一架飞机', 'The new 1954-07 China first plane', '1534785808', '2018-08-28', '04:36:29', '2', '<p>新中国第一架飞机“初教-5”，在南昌飞机制造厂研制成功，首次试飞也取得圆满成功。第一架飞机的成功，是我国在航天领域跨出的重要一步。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> The new Chinese first aircraft &#34;initial -5&#34;, in the Nanchang Aircraft Manufacturing Factory has successfully developed the first test flight, also success. The first aircraft successfully, is an important step in our country in the field of space.</p><p><br/></p>', 192, 104, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(192, '1954-12-25 青藏公路正式通车。', 'The official opening of the Qinghai Tibet highway 1954-12-25.', '1534785851', '2018-08-27', '17:48:46', '2', '<p>1954年12月25日，青藏公路正式通车。这条公路全长1,160千米，全线平均海拔4,000米以上，是世界上海拔最高的公路之一。</p><p>青藏公路改建工程于1975年开工，是世界上尚无先例的高寒冻土区铺设黑色路面工程，共投资7.6亿元，是中国公路史上规模最大的工程。1985年8月青藏公路全线黑色路面铺筑工程基本竣工，大大提高了运输效率，经济效益明显提高，每年可节约运输成本5000万元，行车密度明显提高，最高车流量每昼夜达3000多辆，行车时速由每小时20公里提高到60公里，但还需要对早期铺建的沥青路面、沿线未适应重型车辆的临时性桥涵、多年冻土带热融沉陷及路基翻浆路段进行改建和彻底整治。<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, "pingfang sc", stheiti, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p>', '<p> In December 25, 1954, the official opening of the Qinghai Tibet highway. The road length of 1160 kilometers, across the board average elevation of 4000 meters above the highway is one of the world&#39;s highest.</p><p> The Qinghai Tibet highway reconstruction project started in 1975, is the black pavement engineering laying the world there is no precedent for the alpine permafrost zone, a total investment of 760 million yuan, is the largest in the history of Chinese highway engineering. Across the black pavement August 1985 Qinghai Tibet highway paving project basically completed, greatly improving the transportation efficiency and economic performance improved significantly, a year can save transportation costs 50 million yuan, significantly improve the traffic density, the highest traffic flow of more than 3000 vehicles per day, the driving speed of 20 kilometers per hour to 60 kilometers, but also the need for early asphalt built along the road, did not meet the heavy vehicles temporary bridges and culverts, permafrost thaw settlement and subgrade boiling renovation and overhaul road.<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, "pingfang sc", stheiti, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p>', 197, 51, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(193, '1955-04 周恩来总理率中国代表团出席在印度尼西亚万隆举行的亚非会议。', '1955-04 Zhou Enlai, Prime Minister Chinese rate delegation to attend the meeting held in Indonesia bandung.', '1534785913', '2018-08-28', '04:36:21', '2', '<p>1955年4月，周恩来总理率中国代表团出席在印度尼西亚万隆举行的亚非会议。这是历史上首次由亚非国家自主召开、没有西方殖民国家参加的会议。会议期间，周总理倡导“求同存异”，以和平共处五项原则作为不同社会制度国家之间建立友好合作关系的基础，促成了万隆十项原则的产生。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> On April 1955, Premier Zhou Enlai China delegation to attend the meeting held in Indonesia bandung. This is the first time in the history of Asian and African countries held by independent, no Western colonial countries to participate in the meeting. During the meeting, Premier Zhou advocated the &#34;common ground&#34; and the five principles of peaceful coexistence as the basis for the establishment of friendly relations and cooperation between countries of different social systems, contribute to the formation of the ten principles of bandung.</p><p><br/></p>', 239, 75, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(194, '1955-6 中国与越南民主共和国建交', '1955-6 China and the Democratic Republic of Vietnam established diplomatic relations', '1534786018', '2018-08-21', '01:26:58', 'del', '<p><span style="font-family:宋体">越南民主共和国主席胡志明访华，毛泽东主席到机场迎接。中国是第一个承认越南民主共和国并与之建交的国家。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '<p><span style="font-family:宋体"> The president of the Democratic Republic of Vietnam, President Mao Zedong Hu Zhiming&#39;s visit to the airport. Chinese is the first to admit that the Democratic Republic of Vietnam and establish diplomatic ties with.</span></p><p><br/></p>', 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(195, '1956-04-25 毛泽东作了《论十大关系》的报告', '1956-04-25 Mao Zedong made &#34;on the ten major relationships&#34; Report', '1534786095', '2018-08-21', '01:28:15', 'del', '<p><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">毛泽东作了《论十大关系》的报告</span><span style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">/</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">以毛泽东为代表的中国共产党人开始探索中国自己的社会主义建设道路的标志</span></span></p><p><br/></p>', '<p><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"> Mao Zedong made &#34;on the ten major relationships&#34; Report</span><span style="background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"> /</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"> Mark Mao Zedong as the representative of the Communist Party of China Chinese began to explore their socialist construction road</span></span></p><p><br/></p>', 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(196, '1956-06-07 中国体育史上第一个世界纪录', 'The first 1956-06-07 China sports history world record', '1534786182', '2018-08-28', '04:36:10', '2', '<p>上海陕西南路体育馆，中苏举重友谊比赛中，20岁的广东小伙子陈镜开，以133公斤的挺举，创造了中国体育史上第一个世界纪录。中国从此开始了向着世界体育顶峰的迈进<span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '<p> Shanghai Shaanxi Road stadium, the Sino Soviet friendship weightlifting competitions, the 20 year old boy in Guangdong Chen Jingkai, to 133 kg in the clean and jerk, created the first world record in the history of sports China. China began moving toward the top of the sports world<span style="font-family:宋体"> .</span></p><p><br/></p>', 236, 30, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(197, '1956-07-13 新中国第一辆汽车', 'The new 1956-07-13 China first car', '1534786241', '2018-08-28', '04:36:03', '2', '<p>新中国第一辆汽车——“解放牌”卡车在长春第一汽车制造厂诞生。“长春一汽”是新中国第一家汽车制造厂，建立于1953年7月15日。该厂的第一辆“红旗牌”高级轿车出产于1958年9月28日。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> The new China first car - &#34;Jiefang Truck&#34; in Changchun first automobile factory was born. &#34;Changchun FAW&#34; is a new Chinese first automobile factory, established in July 15, 1953. The first &#34;red card&#34; senior car production in September 28, 1958.</p><p><br/></p>', 294, 57, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(198, '1958-04 开始兴建中国第一个运载火箭发射场。', '1958-04 China began to build the first rocket launch site.', '1534786314', '2018-08-28', '04:35:56', '2', '<p>1958年4月，中国在甘肃酒泉开始兴建中国第一个运载火箭发射场，标志着中国航天第一个自主发射基地的诞生。</p>', '<p> In April 1958, Chinese Chinese began to build the first rocket launch site in Gansu Jiuquan, marking the first independent space launch base of the birth of China.</p>', 186, 81, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(199, '1958-5-17 毛泽东主席在中共八大二次会议上指出：“我们也要搞人造卫星。”', '1958-5-17 President Mao Zedong at the two meeting of the Eighth Party Congress pointed out: &#34;we should also engage satellites.&#34;', '1534786353', '2018-08-21', '01:32:33', 'del', '<p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">毛泽东主席在中共八大二次会议上指出：“我们也要搞人造卫星。”</span></p>', '<p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> President Mao Zedong at the two meeting of the Eighth Party Congress pointed out: &#34;we should also engage satellites.&#34;</span></p>', 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(200, '1959-09-26 大庆油田第一口油井喷射出石油。', '1959-09-26 Daqing, the first oil wells oil injection.', '1534786404', '2018-08-28', '04:35:47', '2', '<p>       1959年9月26日，大庆油田第一口油井喷射出石油。时值国庆10周年，所以该油田以“大庆”命名。1960年，大庆油田开始全面开发，三年后建成世界级大油田，享有“共和国加油机”的美誉。</p><p>      大庆油田是20世纪60～80年代中国最大的油区，它的成功发现和开发，证实了中国学者提出的“陆相地层生油”理论和探矿思想，从而丰富和发展了当代石油地质学理论，彻底甩掉了中国贫油的帽子，改变了中国石油工业落后面貌，使中国石油工业从此走进了历史新纪元，走出一条具有中国石油工业特色的发展道路。</p><p> </p><p><br/></p>', '<p> September 26, 1959 Daqing, the first oil wells oil injection. As the National Day 10th anniversary, so the oil named &#34;Daqing&#34;. In 1960, Daqing oilfield started a comprehensive development, three years after the completion of a world-class oil, enjoy the &#34;Republic of tanker&#34; reputation.</p><p> Daqing oilfield is oilfield Chinese largest in twentieth Century 60~80 time, the success of its discovery and development, confirmed China scholars of the &#34;source&#34; of continental strata theory and prospecting ideas, so as to enrich and develop the theory of petroleum geology, completely get rid of China lean hat, change Chinese oil industry backwardness, the China oil industry came into a new era of history, out of a unique Chinese oil industry development road.</p><p>  </p><p><br/></p>', 282, 48, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(201, '1959-04-05 中国体育史上的第一个世界冠军。', 'The first world champion 1959-04-05 China sports history.', '1534786469', '2018-08-28', '04:35:35', '2', '<p>从香港回到祖国大陆、年仅21岁的运动员容国团，在前联邦德国多特蒙德举行的第25届世界乒乓球锦标赛中，一路过关斩将，奋力夺得了男子单打冠军，这是中国体育史上的第一个世界冠军。</p>', '<p> To return to the mainland, only 21 year old player Rong Guotuan from Hongkong, in the Federal Republic of Germany in Dortmund at the twenty-fifth World Table Tennis Championships, all the way through, to win the men&#39;s singles champion, this is the first world champion in the history of sports China.</p>', 278, 46, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(202, '1960-02-19 中国自行设计制造的试验型液体燃料探空火箭首次发射成功。', '1960-02-19 China self-designed test type liquid fuel rocket manufacturing was successfully launched.', '1534786600', '2018-08-28', '04:35:22', '2', '<p>      1960年2月19日，上海机电设计院自行设计制造的T—7M试验型液体燃料探空火箭，在上海南汇简易发射场试射成功，开始了中国的“空间时代”。这是中国探空火箭技术取得的第一个具有工程实践意义的成果。“T—7M”火箭是院计划研制的“T—7”探空火箭的模型火箭。研制的目的在于掌握火箭设计、制造和试验技术，创造技术保障条件和培养火箭技术队伍，主要用以研究液体燃料火箭的各项技术和摸索火箭发射场的建设经验等。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> February 19, 1960, Shanghai mechanical and electrical design institute to design and manufacture of T - 7M test type liquid fuel rocket launch site in Shanghai, Nanhui, a simple test is successful, the space age began Chinese &#34;&#34;. This is the first of the practical achievements of China sounding rocket technology. &#34;T - 7M&#34; rocket academy plans developed &#34;T - 7&#34; sounding rocket rocket model. The purpose is to understand the rocket design, manufacture and testing technology, technical support and training to create conditions for the rocket team, mainly used to study the liquid fuel rocket technology and exploration launch site construction experience etc..</p><p><br/></p>', 172, 51, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(203, '1960-05-25 中国人第一次站在了世界之颠', '1960-05-25 Chinese first stood on the top of the world', '1534786645', '2018-08-28', '04:35:10', '2', '<p>中国登山运动员王富洲、贡布、屈银华首次登上了海拔8848．13米的世界最高峰——珠穆朗玛峰，这也是人类历史上首次成功地从珠峰北路攀上顶峰。</p><p> </p><p><br/></p>', '<p> China mountaineer Wang Fuzhou, Kampot, Qu Yinhua first appeared on the 8848.13 meters above sea level the highest mountain in the world, the Mount Qomolangma, this is the first time in human history, from the success of Mount Everest Road on top.</p><p>  </p><p><br/></p>', 262, 92, '');
