INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(229, '1981-11-16 中国三大球中的第一个世界冠军', 'The first world champion 1981-11-16 Chinese three ball in', '1534795076', '2018-08-27', '16:14:24', '2', '<p>已经在第三届女排世界杯赛上6战6胜的中国队，迎来了最后的对手日本队。大贩体育馆里日本观众的助威声震耳欲聋，中国队沉着应战，终于以不败的战绩，赢得了中国三大球中的第一个世界冠军。从此后，中国女排屡战屡胜，创造了“五连冠”的奇迹。</p>', '<p> In the third women&#39;s Volleyball World Cup 6 wins out of 6 of the China team, ushered in the last rival Japanese team. Big selling gym Japanese audience cheering was deafening, China team calmly, finally to the unbeaten record, won the first world champion Chinese three ball in. Since then, Chinese women&#39;s volleyball lvzhanlvsheng, created the &#34;Five&#34; miracle.</p>', 281, 47, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(230, '1981-11-20 酵母丙氨酸tRNA人工合成成功', '1981-11-20 yeast alanine tRNA synthesized successfully', '1534795170', '2018-08-27', '16:14:15', '2', '<p>中国科学院上海生物化学研究所王德宝教授等科学家，人工合成了完整的酵母丙氨酸转移核糖核酸，这是世界上第一个人工合成的转移核糖核酸（tRNA）。由于tRNA在蛋白质合成中有着重要作用，而用合成方法改变tRNA的结构以观察对其功能的影响，又是研究tRNA结构与功能的最直接手段，因此酵母丙氨酸tRNA人工合成的成功，在科学上特别在生命起源的研究上有重大意义。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> Professor Wang Debao Chinese Academy of Sciences Shanghai Institute of Biochemistry and other scientists, the complete synthetic yeast alanine transfer RNA, which is the first artificial transfer ribonucleic acid (tRNA) in the world. Because tRNA plays an important role in protein synthesis, and synthesis method of the structure of tRNA in order to observe the effect on its function, but also the most direct means to study the structure and function of tRNA, so the yeast alanine tRNA synthesized successfully, is of great significance in science research especially in the life source.</p><p><br/></p>', 300, 51, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(231, '1982-09 中共十二大，邓小平提出建设有中国特色的社会主义', '1982-09 the twelve National Congress of the CPC, Deng Xiaoping put forward the construction of socialism with China', '1534795281', '2018-08-27', '16:13:57', '2', '<p>中共第十二次全国代表大会的胜利召开，标志着党成功地实现了具有重大历史性意义的伟大转变。 它开始把 中国带入建设有 中国特色的社会主义的新的政治轨道，并以全面开创社会主义现代化建设的新局面而永远载入史册。</p>', '<p> The Twelfth National Congress held a victory, marking the party successfully realized the great transformation is of great historical significance. It began to China into the construction of Chinese socialism political track, and to create a new situation of the socialist modernization construction and go down in history forever.</p>', 288, 89, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(232, '1983-12-22 我国第一台每秒钟运算1亿次以上的计算机——“银河”巨型机研制成功', '1983-12-22 successfully developed China&#39;s first operations per second more than 100 million computer - &#34;the Milky Way&#34; supercomputer', '1534795357', '2018-08-27', '15:45:53', '2', '<p>我国第一台每秒钟运算1亿次以上的计算机——“银河”巨型机由国防科技大学计算机研究所在长沙研制成功。比起国际主流巨型机，“银河”亿次巨型机在10个方面有了创新性进步，使我国成为世界上少数几个拥有巨型计算机的国家之一。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> China&#39;s first operations per second more than 100 million computer - &#34;the Milky Way&#34; supercomputer by National University of Defense Technology Computer Institute Changsha successfully developed. Compared with the international mainstream supercomputers, &#34;the Milky Way&#34; gflop supercomputer in 10 aspects of innovative progress, make our country become one of the few countries in the world have a huge computer.</p><p><br/></p>', 171, 103, '');
