INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(234, '1984-04-08 中国第一颗地球静止轨道试验通信卫星发射成功', '1984-04-08 Chinese first geostationary communication satellite launch test', '1534795498', '2018-08-28', '04:30:02', '2', '<p>1984年4月8日，中国第一颗地球静止轨道试验通信卫星发射成功。十六日，卫星成功地定点于东经一百二十五度赤道上空。中共中央、国务院、中央军委发电致贺。三十日，在北京人民大会堂举行庆祝大会。</p>', '<p> In April 8, 1984, the first test Chinese geostationary communications satellite was successfully launched. Sixteen, the satellite successfully positioned at one hundred and twenty-five degrees east longitude over the equator. The CPC Central Committee and the State Council and the Central Military Commission on power. Thirty, to celebrate the general assembly in Beijing Great Hall of the people.</p>', 222, 57, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(235, '1984-05 开放14个沿海港口城市', '1984-05 open the 14 coastal port city', '1534796359', '2018-08-27', '15:41:51', '2', '<p><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p>沿海开放城市（coastal open city）是指中国沿海地区对外开放的、并在对外经济活动中实行经济特区的某些特殊政策的一系列港口城市，也是经济特区的延伸。</p><p>开放一些沿海开放城市，是根据邓小平的创议而采取的对外开放的又一战略决策。1984年，首批沿海开放城市诞生：大连、秦皇岛、天津、烟台、青岛、连云港、南通、上海、宁波、温州、福州、广州、湛江、北海，被国务院批准为全国第一批对外开放城市。</p><p>中国开放沿海城市的基本目的是为了发挥那里的自然资源优势与经济优势，进一步开展对外经济合作与技术交流，引进外资与先进技术，扩大出口和吸收外汇的能力，加速社会主义现代化的建设。<br/></p>', '<p><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p> The open coastal city (coastal open city) a series of port city refers to the opening of coastal areas, and the implementation of Chinese special zone economy in foreign economic activities, but also the extension of the special economic zones.</p><p> Open the open coastal city, is also a strategic decision based on Deng Xiaoping&#39;s initiative to open. In 1984, the first batch of open coastal city: Dalian, Qinhuangdao, was born in Tianjin, Yantai, Qingdao, Lianyungang, Nantong, Shanghai, Ningbo, Wenzhou, Fuzhou, Guangzhou, Zhanjiang, Beihai, approved by the State Council as the first batch of open city.</p><p> The basic purpose is to open the coastal city of China play where the natural resources and economic advantages, further development of foreign economic cooperation and technological exchanges, the introduction of foreign capital and advanced technology, expand exports and absorb foreign exchange, accelerate the construction of socialist modernization.<br/></p>', 226, 108, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(236, '1984-08-07 中国女排实现', '1984-08-07 China women&#39;s volleyball team to achieve', '1534843224', '2018-08-28', '04:29:51', '2', '<p>1984年第23届奥运会于7月28日至8月11日在美国洛杉矶举行。</p><p>女排比赛于7月30日至8月7日进行。有美国、中国、日本、韩国、秘鲁、巴西、联邦德国、加拿大8支参赛队，分2组进行比赛。</p><p>中国女排在小组赛中以2胜1负成绩排名小组第二进入4强。半决赛战胜日本女排进入决1984年奥运冠军中国队员在领奖台上赛。1984年8月7日，中国女排在第23届洛杉矶奥运会女排决赛中，以3比0战胜美国队，实现“三连冠”。</p>', '<p> The twenty-third Olympic Games in 1984 held in Losangeles from July 28th to August 11th.</p><p> The women&#39;s volleyball competition from July 30th to August 7th. The United States, Japan, South Korea, China, Peru, Brazil, Germany, Canada 8 teams, divided into 2 groups for the game.</p><p> China women&#39;s volleyball team in the group phase with 2 wins and 1 negative results ranked second in the group to enter the top 4. The semifinal victory over Japan&#39;s women&#39;s volleyball team will enter the 1984 Olympic champion Chinese players on the podium match. In August 7, 1984, China women&#39;s volleyball team in the twenty-third Losangeles Olympic Games women&#39;s volleyball final, 3 to 0 victory over the U.S. team, achieve three consecutive years&#34;.</p>', 295, 97, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(237, '1985-02 开辟沿海经济开放区', '1985-02 open open coastal economic zone', '1534843327', '2018-08-21', '17:22:07', 'del', '<p><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">开辟沿海经济开放区</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">(</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">长江三角洲、珠江三角洲、闽南厦门泉州漳州三角地区</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">)</span></p>', '<p><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"> Open coastal economic zone</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"> (</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"> The Yangtze River Delta, Pearl River Delta, Quanzhou Zhangzhou Fujian Xiamen Delta region</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Calibri, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"> )</span></p>', 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(238, '1986-02-01 中国发射一颗实用通信广播卫星', '1986-02-01 China to launch a practical communication broadcasting satellite', '1534843514', '2018-08-28', '04:29:32', '2', '<p>1986年2月1日，中国发射一颗实用通信广播卫星。二十日，卫星定点成功。这标志着中国已全面掌握运载火箭技术，卫星通信由试验阶段进入实用阶段。</p>', '<p> In February 1, 1986, Chinese launch a practical communication broadcasting satellite. Twenty, satellite positioning success. This marks Chinese has a comprehensive grasp of rocket technology, satellite communication entered the practical stage by stage.</p>', 227, 53, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(239, '1986-3-3 批准实施“863计划”', 'The 1986-3-3 approved the implementation of &#34;863 plan&#34;', '1534843636', '2018-08-21', '17:27:16', 'del', '<p>1986-3-3<span style="font-family: 宋体">，王大珩、王淦昌、陈芳允、杨嘉墀</span>4<span style="font-family:宋体">位科学家给邓小平写信，提出要跟踪世界前沿研究，发展我国高科技。这封信得到了国家重视，批准实施</span> <span style="font-family:宋体">了《国家高技术研究发展计划纲要》。因为信件的提交日期，该计划又得名“</span>863<span style="font-family:宋体">计划”。</span>863<span style="font-family:宋体">计划造就了新一代高水平人才，缩小了同世界先进水平的差距，极大地带动了我国高新技术及其产业的发展。</span></p><p> </p><p><span style="font-family:宋体"></span><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '<p> 1986-3-3<span style="font-family: 宋体"> Wang Daheng, Wang Ganchang, Chen Fangyun, Yang Jiachi,</span> Four<span style="font-family:宋体"> The scientists wrote to Deng Xiaoping proposed to research the development of China&#39;s high-tech world tracking. This letter has been national attention, approval and Implementation</span> <span style="font-family:宋体"> The &#34;national high technology research and development program&#34;. Because the letter submitted to date, the program name&#34;</span> Eight hundred and sixty-three<span style="font-family:宋体"> Plan&#34;.</span> Eight hundred and sixty-three<span style="font-family:宋体"> The plan has created a new generation of high level talents, narrowing the gap with the advanced world level, greatly boosted the development of China&#39;s high-tech and high-tech industry.</span></p><p>  </p><p><span style="font-family:宋体"></span><br/></p><p><br/></p>', 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(240, '1987-09-20 我国第一个Internet电子邮件节点正式建成', '1987-09-20 China&#39;s first Internet email node officially completed', '1534843765', '2018-08-28', '04:29:23', '2', '<p>1986年，王运丰教授领导的北京市计算机应用技术研究所实施的国际联网项目——中国学术网（Chinese Academic Network，简称CANET）启动，合作伙伴是德国卡尔斯鲁厄大学维纳•措恩教授带领的科研小组。1987年9月20日，北京计算机应用技术研究所正式建成我国第一个Internet电子邮件节点，连通了Internet的电子邮件系统，并向德国成功发送了第一封电子邮件，内容是“越过长城，走向世界”，揭开了中国人使用互联网的序幕。</p><p> </p><p><br/></p>', '<p> In 1986, the international network - Chinese academic network project implementation of Beijing Institute of computer application technology, led by Professor Wang Yunfeng (the Chinese Academic Network, referred to as CANET) to start, partners are small research group led by Professor Zorn of the University of Karlsruhe in Germany - wiener. In September 20, 1987, Beijing of applied computer technology in China officially opened the first Internet email node, connected to the Internet mail system, and to the success of Germany sent the first e-mail content is over the Great Wall, to the world, opened a prelude to the use of the Internet Chinese.</p><p>  </p><p><br/></p>', 279, 103, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(241, '1987-10 一个中心两个基本点', 'Two basic points: 1987-10 a center', '1534843823', '2018-08-27', '15:05:38', '2', '<p>中共十三大提出社会初级阶段理论和党在社会主义初级阶段的基本路线</p><p></p><p>1987年4月提出基本实现现代化的战略，1987年10月，党的十三大把邓小平“三步走”的发展战略构想确定下来。</p><p>第一步，从1981年到1990年，国民生产总值翻一番，解决人民温饱问题；</p><p>第二步，从1991年到20世纪末，国民生产总值再翻一番，人民生活水平达到小康水平；</p><p>第三步，到21世纪中叶，国民生产总值达到中等发达国家水平，人民生活比较富裕，基本实现现代化。然后，在这个基础上继续前进。</p><p>1997年党的十五大把第三步进一步具体化，提出三个阶段性目标。</p><p>2000年，我们已胜利地实现了“三步走”战略的第一、第二步目标，全国人民的生活总体上达到了小康水平，人均GDP达到848美元，实现了从温饱到小康的历史性跨越。这是中华民族发展史上的一个里程碑。下一步将开始全面建成小康社会，即达到中等发达国家程度的现代化发展战略第三步阶段。</p><p><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><br/></span><br/></p>', '<p> Since the proposed social primary stage theory and the basic line of the party in the primary stage of socialism</p><p></p><p> In April 1987 October 1987, put forward the basic realization of modernization strategy, the party&#39;s thirteenth Congress to finalize the strategic development conception of Deng Xiaoping&#39;s &#34;three step&#34;.</p><p> The first step, from 1981 to 1990, GDP doubled, to solve the problem of food and clothing;</p><p> The second step, from 1991 to the end of twentieth Century, GDP doubled again, the living standards of the people have reached a well-off level;</p><p> The third step to the middle of the twenty-first Century, GDP reached the level of moderately developed countries, people&#39;s lives richer, the basic realization of modernization. Then, continue to move forward on this basis.</p><p> In 1997 the 15th Party Congress made the third step further concrete, put forward three stages of target.</p><p> In 2000, we have successfully implemented the strategy of &#34;three steps&#34;, the first second, the life of the whole people generally reached the well-off level, per capita GDP reached 848 U.S. dollars, has realized the leap from subsistence to a well-off historical. This is a milepost on phylogeny of the Chinese nation. The next step will be to build a well-off society, which reached the degree of medium developed countries in the modernization of the third step development strategy.</p><p><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><br/></span><br/></p>', 346, 87, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(242, '1988 乒乓球首次进入奥运会', '1988 table tennis for the first time in the Olympic Games', '1534843954', '2018-08-27', '15:05:24', '2', '<p>1988年汉城奥运会上，中国选派301名选手参赛，获得5枚金牌、11枚银牌和12枚铜牌，总分数居第8位。88年汉城奥运会，虽然我国只获得5枚金牌，算是滑铁卢，但是奥运健儿还是表现出了惊人的实力，乒乓球首次进入奥运会，陈静就获得单打冠军。</p><p> </p><p><br/></p>', '<p> The 1988 Seoul Olympic Games, Chinese selected 301 players, won 5 gold medals, 11 silver medals and 12 bronze medals, the total score ranked eighth. The 88 Seoul Olympic Games, although China only won 5 gold medals, is Waterloo Olympic athletes, but still showed amazing strength, table tennis for the first time in the Olympic Games, Chen Jing won the singles title.</p><p>  </p><p><br/></p>', 325, 97, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(243, '1988-03-10 中国大陆第一个试管婴儿诞生', '1988-03-10 Chinese, the first test tube baby was born', '1534844009', '2018-08-28', '04:29:13', '2', '<p>1988年3月10日，在北京医科大学第三临床医学院妇产科教授张丽珠等科学家的努力下，中国大陆第一个试管婴儿诞生。这个试管婴儿诞生是我国生殖医学和辅助生育技术向国际先进水平看齐的标志，在我国生殖医学发展史上具有里程碑意义。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> In March 10, 1988, in the Third Affiliated Hospital of Beijing Medical University professor of Obstetrics and Gynecology scientists like Zhang Lizhu&#39;s efforts, the birth of China, the first test tube baby. The test tube baby was born a symbol of China&#39;s reproductive medicine and assisted reproductive technology in line to the international advanced level, has milepost significance in the history of the development of China&#39;s reproductive medicine.</p><p><br/></p>', 216, 36, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(244, '1988-09-07 中国第一颗极地轨道气象卫星。', '1988-09-07 Chinese first polar orbiting meteorological.', '1534844078', '2018-08-28', '04:28:57', '2', '<p>1988年9月7日，在太原卫星发射中心，中国用自行研制的“长征四号”运载火箭成功地发射了第一颗气象卫星。这颗命名为“风云一号”的气象卫星，是中国首次发射的与太阳同步轨道（极地轨道）卫星。在这种轨道上运行的卫星，可观测到地球表面的任何一点，并且每天飞经地球上任何一点上空的地方时不变。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> In September 7, 1988, at the Taiyuan satellite launch center, with Chinese developed the &#34;long four&#34; carrier rocket successfully launched the first meteorological satellite. Meteorological satellite Fengyun named &#34;Fengyun&#34;, is the first launch of the Chinese and sun synchronous orbit (polar orbiting satellite). Run on the track on the satellite, can be observed at any point on the surface of the earth, and every day flying through any point on the earth over the place invariant.</p><p><br/></p>', 336, 99, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(245, '1988-10-16 我国第一座高能加速器——北京正负电子对撞机首次对撞成功。', '1988-10-16 China&#39;s first high energy accelerator of Beijing Electron Positron Collider collider successfully for the first time.', '1534844160', '2018-08-27', '15:03:45', '2', '<p>1988年10月16日，我国第一座高能加速器——北京正负电子对撞机首次对撞成功。正负电子对撞机又称为同步辐射装置，它产生的同步辐射光作为特殊光源，可在生物、医学、化学、材料等领域开展广泛的应用研究工作。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> In October 16, 1988, China&#39;s first high energy accelerator of Beijing Electron Positron Collider collider successfully for the first time. For synchrotron radiation devices called Electron Positron Collider, synchrotron radiation it produces light as a special light source, can carry out extensive application research work in the fields of biology, medicine, chemistry, materials etc..</p><p><br/></p>', 264, 37, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(246, '1988-12-25 中国低纬度区第一次火箭探空试验圆满结束', 'The first rocket test 1988-12-25 Chinese low latitude area ended', '1534844236', '2018-08-21', '17:37:16', 'del', '<p>1988-12-25<span style="font-family: 宋体">，中国科学院海南探空火箭发射场成功地发射了一枚“织女一号”火箭，至此，中国低纬度区第一次火箭探空试验圆满结束。这次为期两周的试验共发射了四枚火箭</span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '<p> 1988-12-25<span style="font-family: 宋体"> Hainan Academy of Sciences, Chinese sounding rocket launching site successfully launched a &#34;VEGA-1 Rockets&#34;, so far, the first rocket test China ended the low latitude area. The two week trial has launched four rockets</span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>', 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(247, '1989-5 中苏关系正常化。', 'The normalization of Sino Soviet relations 1989-5.', '1534844285', '2018-08-21', '17:38:05', 'del', '<p>1989-5<span style="font-family:宋体">，邓小平在会见来访的苏联最高苏维埃主席团主席、苏共中央总书记戈尔巴乔夫时提出，双方本着</span>"<span style="font-family:宋体">结束过去，开辟未来</span>"<span style="font-family:宋体">的精神，实现中苏关系正常化。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '<p> 1989-5<span style="font-family:宋体"> Deng Xiaoping proposed, in a meeting with visiting president of the presidium of the Supreme Soviet, general secretary of the Communist Party Central Committee Gorbachev, the two sides</span> &#34;<span style="font-family:宋体"> The end of the past, opening up the future</span> &#34;<span style="font-family:宋体"> The spirit of the normalization of Sino Soviet relations.</span></p><p><br/></p>', 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(248, '1990-4-7 首次取得了为国外用户发射卫星的圆满成功', '1990-4-7 is the first successful satellite launch for foreign users', '1534844364', '2018-08-21', '17:40:50', 'del', '<p><span style="font-family:宋体"><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;"></span></span></p><p>1990-4-7-21<span style="font-family: 宋体">点</span>30<span style="font-family:宋体">分，中国自行研制的“长征三号”运载火箭在西昌卫星发射中心，把美国制造的亚洲</span>1<span style="font-family:宋体">号通信卫星送入预定的轨道，首次取得了为国外用户发射卫星的圆满成功</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体"></span><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '<p><span style="font-family:宋体"><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;"></span></span></p><p> 1990-4-7-21<span style="font-family: 宋体"> spot</span> Thirty<span style="font-family:宋体"> Chinese, developed the &#34;long three&#34; carrier rocket from the Xichang satellite launch center, the United States made in Asia</span> One<span style="font-family:宋体"> The number of communication satellite, the first successful satellite launch for foreign users</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体"></span><br/></p><p><br/></p>', 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(249, '1991-01-22 中国第一枚一百二十公里高空低纬度探空火箭发射试验成功', '1991-01-22 China first one hundred and twenty kilometers above the low latitude sounding rocket launch test successful', '1534844579', '2018-08-28', '04:22:47', '2', '<p>1991年1月22日下午18点23分中国第一枚一百二十公里高空低纬度探空火箭——“织女三号”在中国科学院海南探空发射场发射试验成功</p>', '<p> On January 22, 1991 at 18:23 in the afternoon Chinese first one hundred and twenty kilometers above the low latitude sounding rocket - &#34;Vega three&#34; launch test success in Chinese Academy of Sciences Hainan sounding</p>', 341, 99, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(250, '1991-12-15 中国大陆第一座核电站——秦山核电站并网发电', '1991-12-15 Chinese, the first nuclear power plant, Qinshan nuclear power plant and power generation', '1534844754', '2018-08-27', '15:02:07', '2', '<p><span style="font-family:宋体"></span></p><p>1991年12月15日，中国大陆第一座核电站——秦山核电站并网发电。这是中国第一座自行设计和建造的30万千瓦商用核电站，标志着中国已掌握了核电技术，成为世界上继美国、英国、法国、前苏联、加拿大、瑞典之后第七个能够独立设计制造核电站的国家。</p><p><span style="font-family:宋体"></span><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '<p><span style="font-family:宋体"></span></p><p> In December 15, 1991, Chinese, the first nuclear power plant, Qinshan nuclear power plant and power generation. This is the first China designed and built 300 thousand KW commercial nuclear power plant, marking the China have mastered nuclear technology, become the world after the United States, Britain, France, the former Soviet Union, Canada, Sweden seventh independently design and manufacture of nuclear power plant state.</p><p><span style="font-family:宋体"></span><br/></p><p><br/></p>', 338, 32, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(251, '1992-10 建立中国社会主义市场经济体制', '1992-10 the establishment of the socialist market economic system Chinese', '1534845047', '2018-08-21', '17:55:48', 'del', '<p><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">中共十四大，建立中国社会主义市场经济体制，确立了邓小平建设有中国特色社会主义理论在全党的指导地位</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体"></span><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '<p><span style="font-family: 宋体; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"> The 14th National Congress of CPC, Chinese established the socialist market economic system, the establishment of Deng Xiaoping theory of building socialism with Chinese characteristics in the guiding position</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体"></span><br/></p><p><br/></p>', 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(252, '1992-11-19 “银河—Ⅱ”计算机研制成功。', 'The successful development of 1992-11-19 &#34;- the Milky Way II computer.', '1534845392', '2018-08-27', '15:01:31', '2', '<p>1992年11月19日，“银河—Ⅱ”计算机研制成功。银河Ⅱ型巨型计算机，由国防科学技术大学与国家气象中心一起研制成功。每秒运算10亿次，它的出现使中国成为当今世界少数几个能发布中期数值预报的国家。</p>', '<p> In November 19, 1992, the successful development of the Milky Way II computer. The Milky Way type II supercomputer, by the national defense science and Technology University and the National Meteorological Center developed together. 1 billion operations per second, it appears that China become one of the world&#39;s few countries can publish medium-term numerical forecast.</p>', 300, 74, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(253, '1993-8 中国开始在国际纳米科技领域占有一席之地', '1993-8 Chinese began to occupy a space for one person in the international field of nano science and technology', '1534862494', '2018-08-21', '22:41:34', 'del', '<p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">中国科学院北京真空物理实验室（现为中国科学院物理所纳米物理与器件实验室）庞世瑾等科学家操纵原子，成功写出“中国”二字，标志着中国开始在国际纳米科技领域占有一席之地。</span></p>', '<p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> China Academy of Sciences Beijing Laboratory of Vacuum Physics (now Chinese Physics Institute of nanoscale physics and Devices Laboratory) Shijin Pang and other scientists manipulating atoms, write two words &#34;China&#34; success, marking the China began to occupy a space for one person in the international field of nano science and technology.</span></p>', 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(254, '1994-02-22 中国第一座海事卫星地面站通过验收。', '1994-02-22 Chinese first maritime satellite ground station through the acceptance of.', '1534862615', '2018-08-21', '22:43:35', 'del', '<p><span style="font-family:宋体">一九九四年二月二十二日，中国第一座海事卫星地面站通过验收。它的建成填补了中国高科技的一项空白。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '<p><span style="font-family:宋体"> In February 22, 1994, the first Chinese maritime satellite ground station through the acceptance of. It&#39;s built to fill a gap in China high-tech.</span></p><p><br/></p>', 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(255, '1994-04 中国正式接入国际互联网', '1994-04 Chinese formal access to the Internet', '1534862676', '2018-08-28', '04:22:37', '2', '<p>      1994年4月，正式接入国际互联网.。中国国家计算与网络设施NCFC工程连入Internet的64K国际专线开通，实现了与Internet的全功能连接。从此，中国正式成为真正拥有全功能Internet的国家</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> April 1994, formal access to the Internet. Chinese National Computing and network infrastructure engineering NCFC connected to the Internet 64K international line opened, the connection with the function of Internet. Since then, Chinese officially became the country really have a full-featured Internet</p><p><br/></p>', 318, 85, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(256, '1997-07-01 祖国对香港恢复行使主权', '1997-07-01 China resumed the exercise of sovereignty over Hongkong', '1534862748', '2018-08-28', '04:22:25', '2', '<p>      1997年7月1日对香港恢复行使主权，英国将在同时将香港交还给中国。1984年9月26日，中英两国政府在北京草签关于香港问题的联合声明和三个附件。</p><p>声明宣布，中国政府决定，1997年7月1日对香港恢复行使主权，英国将在同时将香港交还给中国。联合声明还宣布了中国政府对香港恢复行使主权后设立直辖于中央人民政府的香港特别行政区，除外交和国防事务属于中央管理外，特别行政区享有高度自治权，包括行政管理权、立法权、独立的司法和终审权，现行法律基本不变；特别行政区政府由当地人组成，生活方式不变；保持自由港、独立关税地区和国际金融中心的地位等共12条。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> July 1, 1997 resumed the exercise of sovereignty over Hongkong in the UK will also give the Hongkong back to Chinese. In September 26, 1984, the two governments signed a joint statement on the question of Hongkong and three accessories in Beijing.</p><p> The statement declared, China government decided to resume the exercise of sovereignty over Hongkong in July 1, 1997, Britain will at the same time will return Hongkong to Chinese. The joint statement also announced that the China government resumed the exercise of sovereignty over Hongkong after the establishment of directly under the Central People&#39;s Government of the Hongkong Special Administrative Region, except in foreign and defence affairs belongs to the central management, special administrative region with a high degree of autonomy, including the administrative, legislative and independent judicial power and the current law, essentially the same government; the Special Administrative Region by the local people. The way of life; to maintain a free port, a separate customs territory and an international financial centre and a total of 12.</p><p><br/></p>', 325, 97, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(257, '1997-0９-12~18 中国共产党第十五次全国代表大会在北京召开', '1997-09-12~18 Chinese Fifteenth National Congress of the Communist Party held in Beijing', '1534862919', '2018-08-28', '04:22:09', '2', '<p>中国共产党第十五次全国代表大会高举邓小平理论伟大旗帜，总结了我国改革和建设的新经验，把邓小平理论确定为党的指导思想，把依法治国确定为治国的基本方略，把坚持公有制为主体、多种所有制经济共同发展，坚持按劳分配为主体、多种分配方式并存，确定为我国在社会主义初级阶段的基本经济制度和分配制度。党和十五大对建设有中国特色的社会主义事业的跨世纪发展作出了全面部署。</p><p><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span><br/></p>', '<p> The great banner of Deng Xiaoping theory Chinese Fifteenth National Congress of the Communist party hold, summarizes the new experience of China&#39;s reform and construction, the Deng Xiaoping theory as the guiding ideology of the party, the rule of law as a basic strategy of governing the country, to adhere to public ownership, the common development of multi ownership economy, stick with distribution according to work as the main body, a variety of modes of distribution, determined to be in the primary stage of socialism basic economic system and distribution system in china. The deployment of a comprehensive cross century development of the party and the Congress have China characteristic to the construction of the socialist cause.</p><p><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;"></span><br/></p>', 283, 111, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(258, '1997-06-19 国防科技大学研制的“银河—Ⅲ”并行巨型计算机在京通过国家鉴定', '1997-06-19 developed by National University of Defense Technology &#34;the Milky Way III&#34; parallel supercomputers in Beijing through national identification', '1534863171', '2018-08-28', '04:21:54', '2', '<p>1997年，运算130亿次/秒的“银河—Ⅲ”计算机研制成功, 1997年6月19日，由国防科技大学研制的“银河—Ⅲ”并行巨型计算机在京通过国家鉴定。该机采用分布式共享存储结构，面向大型科学与工程计算和大规模数据处理，基本字长64位，峰值性能为130亿次。该机有多项技术居国内领先，综合技术达到当前国际先进水平。</p>', '<p> In 1997, 13 billion times / sec operation &#34;of the Milky Way&#34; computer was developed in June 19, 1997, developed by National University of Defense Technology, &#34;the Milky Way III&#34; parallel supercomputers in Beijing through national identification. This machine adopts the distributed shared memory structure for large-scale scientific and Engineering Computing and massive data processing, the basic 64 bit word length, peak performance of 13 billion. The machine has a number of domestic leading technology, integrated technology reached the international advanced level.</p>', 267, 66, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(259, '1998-5-2 中国自行研制生产的“长二丙”改进型运载火箭在太原卫星发射中心发射成功。', '1998-5-2 China developed production of &#34;Changerbing&#34; improved rocket from the Taiyuan Satellite Launch Center Launch success.', '1534863241', '2018-08-21', '22:54:01', 'del', '<p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">1998-5-2</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">，中国自行研制生产的“长二丙”改进型运载火箭在太原卫星发射中心发射成功。这标志着中国具有参与国际中低轨道商业发射市场竞争力。</span></p>', '<p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;"> 1998-5-2</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> China, self-developed production of &#34;Changerbing&#34; improved rocket from the Taiyuan Satellite Launch Center Launch success. This marks the Chinese low orbit can participate in international commercial launching market competitiveness.</span></p>', 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(260, '1999-9 中国加入人类基因组计划', 'Adding 1999-9 of the human genome project China', '1534863308', '2018-08-21', '22:55:08', 'del', '<p>1999-9<span style="font-family:宋体">，中国加入人类基因组计划，负责测定人类基因组全部序列的</span>1%<span style="font-family:宋体">，也就是三号染色体上的三千万个碱基对。中国是第六个参与国，也是参与这一研究计划的唯一发展中国家。</span>2000-6-26-<span style="font-family:宋体">，参与人类基因组计划的美、英、德、日、法、中六国联合宣布，人类基因组工作框架图绘制完成。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '<p> 1999-9<span style="font-family:宋体"> China, joined the human genome project, responsible for the determination of the whole human genome sequence</span> 1%<span style="font-family:宋体"> That is, thirty million on chromosome three base pairs. Chinese is only sixth participating countries, developing countries is also involved in the research project.</span> 2000-6-26-<span style="font-family:宋体"> In the human genome project, America, Britain, Germany, Japan, France and six jointly announced that the human genome mapping framework to complete the work.</span></p><p><br/></p>', 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(261, '1999-11-20 中国第一艘试验飞船“神舟”一号首发成功，中国成为继美、俄之后世界上第三个拥有载人航天技术的国家。', '1999-11-20 Chinese first experimental spacecraft &#34;Shenzhou&#34; on the initial success, Chinese become after the United States and Russia in third world countries have manned space technology.', '1534863370', '2018-08-27', '14:58:59', '2', '<p>1999-11-20，中国第一艘无人试验飞船“神舟”一号飞船在酒泉起飞，21小时后在内蒙古中部回收场成功着陆，圆满完成“处女之行”。这次飞行成功为中国载人飞船上天打下非常坚实的基础。在完成了21个小时的空间科学试验后，于21日3时41分成功着陆。“神舟”号试验飞船的成功发射和回收，成为中国航天史上的又一里程碑。</p>', '<p> 1999-11-20, Chinese first unmanned experimental spacecraft &#34;Shenzhou&#34; spacecraft in the 21 hours after takeoff, landing in central Mongolia recycling field, the successful completion of the virgin tour&#34;. This flight is very solid foundation Chinese successfully launched the manned spaceship. After the completion of the space science experiment after 21 hours, 21 to 3:41 on the landing. &#34;The successful launch and recovery of the Shenzhou spacecraft, become a milepost in the history of space flight Chinese.</p>', 311, 53, '');
