lobal economic development, China ushered in a golden period.</span></p><p> Two thousand and one<span style="font-family:宋体"> year</span> Eleven<span style="font-family:宋体"> month</span> Ten<span style="font-family:宋体"> In Japan, the World Trade Organization (held in Doha, Qatar</span> WTO<span style="font-family:宋体"> ) the Fourth Ministerial Conference of the China joined the world trade organization, legal documents, marking the China finally became a new member of the world trade organization.</span> Two thousand and one<span style="font-family:宋体"> year</span> Eleven<span style="font-family:宋体"> month</span> Twenty<span style="font-family:宋体"> WTO, the director general Michael Moore sent a letter to members of the WTO, announced that the Chinese government has to</span> Two thousand and one<span style="font-family:宋体"> year</span> Eleven<span style="font-family:宋体"> month</span> Eleven<span style="font-family:宋体"> To accept the &#34;Protocol&#34; China joined WTO, the protocol will be</span> Twelve<span style="font-family:宋体"> month</span> Eleven<span style="font-family:宋体"> Date, China will officially become a member of the WTO on the same day.</span> Two thousand and one<span style="font-family:宋体"> year</span> Twelve<span style="font-family:宋体"> month</span> Eleven<span style="font-family:宋体"> On China&#39;s accession to the World Trade Organization</span> (WTO)<span style="font-family:宋体"> As the article.</span> One hundred and forty-three<span style="font-family:宋体"> A member of.</span></p><p><br/></p>', 359, 44, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(268, '2001-06-15 上海合作组织在上海正式成立，进一步加强了中国与周边国家的关系。', '2001-06-15 Shanghai cooperation organization was formally established in Shanghai, to further strengthen the relations with neighboring countries Chinese.', '1534864871', '2018-08-28', '04:21:36', '2', '<p>2001年6月15日上海合作组织在上海正式成立。上海合作组织的前身是上海五国会晤机制。上海合作组织起源于1996年，是中国、俄罗斯、哈萨克斯坦、吉尔吉斯斯坦、塔吉克斯坦的关于加强边境地区信任和裁军的谈判进程的组织。上海合作组织是第一个以中国城市命名的国际组织，它进一步加强了中国与周边国家的关系。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> In June 15, 2001 the Shanghai cooperation organization was formally established in Shanghai. The Shanghai cooperation organization is the predecessor of Shanghai five meeting mechanism. The Shanghai cooperation organization founded in 1996, is China, on the strengthening of trust and disarmament negotiations in the border areas of Russia, Kazakhstan, Kyrgyzstan, the organization of Tajikistan. Shanghai cooperation organization is the first to be named after Chinese city international organization, it further strengthened relations with neighboring countries Chinese.</p><p><br/></p>', 222, 77, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(269, '2001-07-13 北京成功获得2008年奥运会举办权', '2001-07-13 Beijing successfully won the right to host the 2008 Olympic Games', '1534866177', '2018-08-28', '04:20:47', '2', '<p>      北京成功获得2008年奥运会举办权。2001年7月13日是个举国欢腾的日子，中国在首次申办奥运会失利八年后，终于申奥成功，赢得了2008年奥运会举办权，使中国人的百年梦想最终得以实现。（中国奥运梦想历程：中国申奥大事记 1908年，中国一本名为《天津青年》的杂志曾向国人提出过三个问题：中国何时才能派一位选手参加奥运会？中国何时才能派一支队伍参加奥运会？中国何时才能举办奥运会？从1908年到2008年整整100年。中国人已将之变为事实）</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> Beijing successfully won the right to host the 2008 Olympic games. July 13, 2001 is a day of jubilation, Chinese in the first bid for the Olympic Games lost after eight years, finally the success of the Olympic bid, won the right to host the 2008 Olympic Games, the Chinese finally realized the dream of a century. China (Olympic dream journey: Chinese Olympic memorabilia in 1908, China a book entitled &#34;Tianjin youth&#34; magazine Xiangguo had raised three questions: when can China sent a player to participate in the Olympic Games? When can Chinese send a team to participate in the Olympic Games? When can China Olympic Games? From 1908 to 2008 for 100 years. Chinese already will become reality)</p><p><br/></p>', 257, 63, '');
