INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(277, '2005-12-10 洋山深水港区（一期工程）顺利开港，为中国最大的集装箱深水港。', '2005-12-10 of Yangshan Deepwater Port (a project) successfully opened in Hong Kong, for China largest container harbor.', '1534896878', '2018-08-22', '19:12:10', 'del', '<p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">洋山深水港位于杭州湾口、长江口外的浙江省嵊泗崎岖列岛（洋山景区），由大、小洋山等数十个岛屿组成。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">2005</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">年</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">12</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">月</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">10</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">日，洋山深水港启用仪式在一期工程码头隆重举行。</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">06</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">年，二期、三期工程相继完工，规划到</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">2020</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">年，北港区（小洋山一侧）可形成</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">10</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">公里左右深水岸线，洋山港布置集装箱深水泊位</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">50</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">多个，设计年吞吐能力</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">1500</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">万标准箱（</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;serif&#39;">TEU</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">）以上，届时将成为上海最大的港口中心。</span><span style="font-family:宋体"></span></p><p><br/></p>', '<p><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体"> Yangshan deep water harbor is located at the mouth of Hangzhou Bay, Yangtze River Estuary of Zhejiang province Shengsi (Yangshan scenic area), Qiqu Archipelago consists of large and small Yangshan dozens of island