INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(278, '2006-05-20 长江三峡水利枢纽工程全线建成', 'The full range of 2006-05-20 the Three Gorges Project', '1534936666', '2018-08-28', '04:19:36', '2', '<p><span style="font-family: ">  </span>    二十日下午十四时，三峡大坝最后一仓混凝土浇筑完毕，举世瞩目的三峡大坝全线到达设计高程一百八十五米。这标志着世界上最大的水利枢纽工程中国长江三峡水利枢纽主体工程完工。兴建三峡工程可实现三大效益：可使长江中下游河段防洪标准由不足十年一遇提高百年一遇，保护长江中下游至少一千五百万人口和一百五十万公顷耕地。利用工三峡大坝挡水发电，可有效缓解中国华中、华东、广东等地区用电紧张局面，促进中国电力联网和南北互供、西电东送输电格局形成。在三峡水库蓄水后，长江航运条件在可大大改善，运输成本也得到有效降低，使长江成为名副其实的“黄金水道”。</p><p>      三峡工程”是世界上工程量最大、难度最大、施工期流量最大的水利工程。大坝全长2309米，设计高程达到海拔185米，是世界上规模最大的混凝土重力坝。1820万千瓦的装机容量和847亿千瓦时的-发电量也居世界第一。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p><span style="font-family: ">  </span> Twenty at fourteen PM, the last position in Three Gorges dam concrete pouring, the Three Gorges dam across the board to design height of one hundred and eighty-five meters. This marks the world&#39;s largest water control project Chinese Yangtze River Three Gorges project main project completed. The construction of the Three Gorges project can achieve three major benefits: the flood control standard in the Yangtze River downstream from less than ten years to improve the hundred years, the protection of the Yangtze River at least fifteen million people and one million and five hundred thousand hectares of arable land. The use of the Three Gorges dam water retaining power, can effectively alleviate the power shortage situation in central and eastern China, Guangdong and other regions China, promote China power interconnection and mutual supply between South and North and west to east transmission pattern. In the Three Gorges reservoir, the Yangtze River shipping conditions can greatly improve, transportation costs are effectively reduced, to become worthy of the name &#34;golden waterway of Yangtze river&#34;.</p><p> Three Gorges project is the world&#39;s largest project, the most difficult, the largest flow of water conservancy project construction period. The dam is 2309 meters, the design height reached an altitude of 185 meters, is the world&#39;s largest concrete dam. Electricity installed capacity of 84 billion 700 million KW and 18 million 200 thousand KW - is also ranked first in the world.</p><p><br/></p>', 309, 87, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(279, '2006-07-01 青藏铁路全线建成并通车', '2006-07-01 the Qinghai Tibet railway was completed and opened to traffic', '1534936778', '2018-08-28', '04:08:30', '2', '<p>2006年7月1日，经过10万筑路大军历时5年的艰苦奋战，青藏铁路格尔木至拉萨段建成，至此世界上海拔最高、线路最长的青藏铁路全面建成胜利通车！</p><p>      青藏铁路西宁至拉萨全长1956公里，是世界上海拔最高、线路最长、穿越冻土里程最长的高原铁路。建设青藏铁路是几代中国人梦寐以求的愿望。新中国成立不久，国家有关部门就着手研究进藏铁路问题。1958年，青藏铁路一期工程西宁至格尔木段开工，1984年交付运营。但是，限于当时国家的经济实力和高原、冻土等筑路技术难题尚未解决，格尔木至拉萨段被迫停建。1994年7月，中共中央召开第三次西藏工作座谈会后，铁道部对进藏铁路进行多方案选线，提出首选青藏铁路建设的建议。2001年2月，中共中央、国务院批准建设青藏铁路二期工程格尔木至拉萨段。青藏铁路格尔木至拉萨段全长1142公里，海拔4000米以上的地段达960公里，最高点海拔5072米，经过连续多年冻土地段550公里，是世界铁路建设史上最具挑战性的工程项目。2001年6月，青藏铁路格尔木至拉萨段正式开工建设。各参建单位和广大铁路建设者顽强拼搏，勇克难关，破解了多年冻土、高寒缺氧、生态脆弱三大世界性工程技术难题，创造了多项世界铁路之最。2006年7月1日，青藏铁路建成并实现全线通车试运营。青藏铁路的建成通车，对于青藏两省区加快经济社会发展、改善各族群众生活，增进民族团结和巩固祖国边防，都具有十分重大的意义。</p>', '<p> In July 1, 2006, after 100 thousand road army after 5 years of hard work, the Qinghai Tibet Railway Geermu Lasa section was built, so far the highest and longest in the world into a comprehensive victory in the opening of the Qinghai Tibet railway!</p><p> Qinghai Tibet railway from Xining to Lhasa, a total length of 1956 kilometers, is the world&#39;s highest and longest, through the frozen earth the longest plateau railway mileage. The construction of Qinghai Tibet railway is the dream of several generations of Chinese. The new Chinese established, the relevant departments of the state had begun to study the problems in Tibet railway. In 1958, a period of Qinghai Tibet railway project from Xining to Golmud section started delivery operation in 1984. However, at the time the country&#39;s economic strength and plateau, permafrost and other road technical problems have not been resolved, Golmud to Lhasa was forced to halt. In July 1994, the CPC Central Committee held the Third Forum on work in Tibet, the Ministry of railway to Tibet railway line selection scheme is proposed, the preferred Qinghai Tibet railway construction proposal. In February 2001, the CPC Central Committee, the State Council approved the construction of Qinghai Tibet Railway Golmud to Lhasa section of the two phase of the project. The Qinghai Tibet railway from Golmud to Lhasa is 1142 kilometers long, 4000 meters above the sea level, the area of 960 km, the highest point 5072 meters above sea level, through the continuous permafrost area of 550 km, is the most challenging project of railway construction history worldwide. In June 2001, the Qinghai Tibet railway from Golmud to Lhasa officially started construction. The construction units and the railway builders tenaciously, Junker difficulties, break the permafrost, alpine, ecological fragile three engineering problems, to create a number of the world&#39;s railway. In July 1, 2006, the Qinghai Tibet railway was completed and opened to traffic trial operation. The Qinghai Tibet railway was opened to traffic, the two provinces for accelerating economic and social development and improve the lives of people of all ethnic groups, to promote national unity and consolidate the border, have great significance.</p>', 241, 99, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(280, '2007-10-24 我国第一颗绕月探测卫星——“嫦娥一号”发射成功，并进入预定地球轨道', '2007-10-24 China&#39;s first lunar orbiter -- Chang&#39;e-1 successfully launched, and entered the preset orbit', '1534937417', '2018-08-27', '10:31:46', '2', '<p>2007-10-24，我国第一颗绕月探测卫星——“嫦娥一号”发射成功，并进入预定地球轨道。“嫦娥”的月球之行担负了四大任务：绘制立体的-球地图；探测月球上元素的分布；评估月球上土壤的厚度和氦-3的资源量以及记录原始太阳风数据。11-26-，国家航天局公布了第一张“嫦娥”拍摄的月球照片。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> 2007-10-24, China&#39;s first lunar orbiter -- Chang&#39;e-1 successfully launched, and entered the preset orbit. Chang&#39;e moon has four major tasks: draw - ball map three-dimensional distribution of elements on the moon; detection; evaluation of soil thickness and the amount of -3 helium resources on the moon and a record of the original solar wind data. 11-26-, NASA released photos of the moon first &#34;Moon&#34; shot.</p><p><br/></p>', 310, 44, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(281, '2008-08-08 北京奥运会开幕', '2008-08-08 the opening ceremony of Beijing Olympic Games', '1534937779', '2018-08-28', '04:04:34', '2', '<p>北京奥运会，这是中国人在家门口举办的第一届奥运会，全民助奥，全民健身，中国体育代表团，总算扬眉吐气，以51金，17银，14铜的傲人成绩雄踞金牌榜首位，全面改写奥运历史，逐渐实现，由体育大国向体育强国的转变。</p><p> </p><p><br/></p>', '<p> The Beijing Olympic Games, this is Chinese at home for the first Olympic Games, Olympic National Fitness, help, China sports delegation, was a feeling of exaltation upon fulfillment with 51 gold, 17 silver, 14 bronze, the proud achievements in gold medals, a complete rewrite of Olympic history, gradually realize the transformation from physical power to, sports power.</p><p>  </p><p><br/></p>', 255, 52, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(282, '2008-09-25 神舟七号 2008-09-25-首次承载三名宇航员进入太空', '2008-09-25 2008-09-25- for the first time, the Shenzhou seven carrying three astronauts into space', '1534938266', '2018-08-26', '08:08:16', '2', '<p>舟七号 2008年09月25日首次承载三名宇航员进入太空，承载的宇航员是翟志刚、刘伯明和景海鹏， 成功进行出舱活动（又称太空行走）。2008年9月25日，我国自行研制的“神舟七号”载人飞船在酒泉卫星发射中心发射升空，并准确进入预定轨道。9月27日，航天员翟志刚打开神舟七号载人飞船轨道舱舱门，首度实施空间出舱活动。这是我国航天员首次实现太空</p>', '<p> Boat No. seven 2008 09 25 August for the first time, carrying three astronauts into space, carrying astronauts Zhai Zhigang, Liu Boming and Jing Haipeng, the success of the extravehicular activities (also known as space walk). In September 25, 2008, China&#39;s self-developed Shenzhou seven manned spacecraft at the Jiuquan satellite launch center, and accurately into orbit. On September 27th, astronaut Zhai Zhigang opened the Shenzhou seven manned spacecraft orbit cabin door, for the first time in the implementation of space extravehicular activities. This is China&#39;s first astronaut in space</p>', 176, 97, '');
