INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(308, '2017-07-30 建军90周年举行盛大阅兵', '2017-07-30 90th anniversary army held a grand parade', '1535160845', '2018-08-28', '04:01:29', '2', '<p>7月30日上午，庆祝中国人民解放军建军90周年阅兵在朱日和联合训练基地隆重举行。中共中央总书记、国家主席、中央军委主席习近平检阅部队并发表重要讲话。1.2万名受阅官兵、600多台受阅车辆装备集结列阵，100多架战机在6个机场整装编队。这是中国人民解放军首次以庆祝建军节为主题的盛大阅兵，是野战化、实战化的沙场点兵，是人民军队整体性、革命性变革后的全新亮相。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> The morning of July 30th, China celebrate the people&#39;s Liberation Army Parade was held in 90th anniversary and joint training base zhu. The general secretary of the CPC Central Committee, state president and CMC Chairman Xi Jinping inspected the troops and delivered an important speech. 12 thousand soldiers, more than 600 by the reading by reading the vehicle equipment assembly array, more than 100 aircraft in 6 airports. The formation. This is the first time to celebrate China people&#39;s Liberation Army army day as the theme of the grand parade, is a field, combat the soldiers on the battlefield, is the people&#39;s army, the whole revolutionary change after the new appearance.</p><p><br/></p>', 274, 97, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(309, '2017-10-18~10-24 国共产党第十九次全国代表大会（简称党的十九大）在北京召开。', '2017-10-18~10-24 in the nineteenth National Congress of the Communist Party (the nineteen party) held in Beijing.', '1535160919', '2018-08-26', '07:58:25', '2', '<p>党的十九大是在全面建成小康社会关键阶段、中国特色社会主义发展关键时期召开的一次十分重要的大会，对鼓舞和动员全党全国各族人民继续推进全面建成小康社会、坚持和发展中国特色社会主义具有重大意义。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> The nineteen party is fully completed in the key stage of a well-off society, the key period of socialist development China held a very important meeting, continue to promote the comprehensive well-off society, adhere to and development is of great significance Chinese characteristic socialism to inspire and mobilize the whole Party and the people of all ethnic groups.</p><p><br/></p>', 200, 72, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(310, '2018-05-05 马克思诞辰200周年纪念日。', '2018-05-05 Marx birthday 200th anniversary anniversary.', '1535160992', '2018-08-28', '04:01:19', '2', '<p>纪念马克思诞辰200周年大会4日上午在北京人民大会堂隆重举行。中共中央总书记、国家主席、中央军委主席习近平在会上发表重要讲话强调，我们纪念马克思，是为了向人类历史上最伟大的思想家致敬，也是为了宣示我们对马克思主义科学真理的坚定信念。</p><p>人类历史上各种各样的宣言不计其数，但没有一个能够像《共产党宣言》那样，在它发表170年的时间里，始终对于推进人类社会发展进程发挥着巨大作用，至今仍然闪耀着并且还将继续闪耀着指导社会发展实践的不朽光芒。它所揭示的真理、它所指引的目标，它所推崇的价值、它所坚持的原则、它所贯穿的方法、它所饱含的激情，今天依然激励着、指引着千百万人坚定不移地奋斗实践。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> In memory of Marx&#39;s 200th anniversary conference held in Beijing Great Hall of the people on the morning of 4. The general secretary of the CPC Central Committee, state president and CMC Chairman Xi Jinping delivered an important speech at the meeting stressed that we commemorate Marx, to the history of mankind&#39;s greatest thinkers tribute, but also to declare our belief in Marx&#39;s scientific truth.</p><p> In human history, a variety of declaration, but no one can be too many to count, like the &#34;Communist Manifesto&#34;, it was published in 170 years, has always been to promote the development of human society plays a huge role, still shining and will continue to shine a light guide immortal social development practice. It reveals the truth, it leads the goal, it respected the value, it adheres to the principle, it runs through the method, it is full of passion, today still inspires and guides millions of people struggle unswervingly practice.</p><p><br/></p>', 206, 36, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(311, '2018-5-18 中国真正意义上的第一艘国产航空母舰完成首次海上试验任务，即将返回大连造船厂码头', '2018-5-18 China the true meaning of the first indigenous aircraft carrier completed the first sea trial task, will return to the Dalian shipyard dock', '1535161107', '2018-08-25', '09:38:27', 'del', '<p>001A<span style="font-family:宋体">型航空母舰是中国首艘自主建造的国产航母，基于对前苏联库兹涅佐夫级航空母舰、中国辽宁号航空母舰的研究，由中国自行改进研发而成，是中国真正意义上的第一艘国产航空母舰。</span></p><p><br/></p>', '<p> 001A<span style="font-family:宋体"> Aircraft carrier is Chinese&#39;s first self built aircraft carriers, the research of the former Soviet Union Kuznetsov class aircraft carrier USS Liaoning, China based on Chinese by improved research and development, Chinese is the true meaning of the first indigenous aircraft carrier.</span></p><p><br/></p>', 0, 0, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(312, '2018 北斗卫星导航系统在2018年底要发射18颗左右的卫星，可以优先为“一带一路”国家和地区提供服务。', '2018 Beidou satellite navigation system to launch about 18 satellites at the end of 2018, can give priority to &#34;The Belt and Road&#34; countries and regions to provide services.', '1535161164', '2018-08-26', '07:58:04', '2', '<p>北斗卫星导航系统在2018年底要发射18颗左右的卫星，可以优先为“一带一路”国家和地区提供服务。2020年底前建成30颗卫星的完整系统，提供全球服务。</p><p>　目前，我国已经推出全球首个支持北斗的加速辅助定位系统，服务覆盖200多个国家和地区，用户已经突破1亿，日服务达2亿次。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> Beidou satellite navigation system to launch about 18 satellites at the end of 2018, can give priority to &#34;The Belt and Road&#34; countries and regions to provide services. By the end of 2020 to build a complete system of 30 satellites to provide global services.</p><p> At present, our country has launched the world&#39;s first to support Beidou Positioning System accelerated auxiliary service, covering more than 200 countries and regions, the user has exceeded 100 million, up to 200 million times daily service.</p><p><br/></p>', 262, 97, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(313, '2020 工业污染源全面达标排放计划', '2020 industrial comprehensive pollution discharge standards plan', '1535161219', '2018-08-26', '07:57:50', '2', '<p>2020年,工业污染源全面达标排放计划，我们所有工业污染源到2020年都必须要做到达标排放，不达标的不能排放。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> In 2020, industrial comprehensive pollution discharge standards, all industrial pollution sources by 2020 must meet emissions standards, non-compliance can not discharge.</p><p><br/></p>', 322, 105, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(314, '2020 全国农作物耕种收综合机械化水平达到68%以上', '2020 of the crop harvesting mechanization level reached more than 68%', '1535161508', '2018-08-26', '07:57:37', '2', '<p>到2020年，力争全国农作物耕种收综合机械化水平达到68%以上，其中三大粮食作物耕种收综合机械化水平均达到80%以上，机械化植保防治、机械化秸秆处理和机械化烘干处理水平有大幅度提升。</p>', '<p> By 2020, strive to national crop harvesting mechanization level reached more than 68%, of which three major grain crops mechanized farming income level reached more than 80%, the mechanization of plant protection, mechanized straw processing and drying mechanization level has greatly improved.</p>', 256, 48, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(315, '2020 实现欧洲和亚洲之间的洲际量子保密通信', '2020 intercontinental quantum secure communication between Europe and Asia', '1535161636', '2018-08-26', '07:57:22', '2', '<p>2020年实现欧洲和亚洲之间的洲际量子保密通信。今后我国还将陆续发射多颗量子卫星，力争在2020年实现欧洲和亚洲之间的洲际量子保密通信，在2030年前后率先建成全球一体化的广域量子保密通信网络。</p>', '<p> 2020 intercontinental quantum secure communication between Europe and asia. In the future China will continue to launch a multi quantum satellite, and strive in 2020 to achieve intercontinental quantum secure communication between Europe and Asia, in 2030 after the first to build a wide quantum secure communication network of global integration.</p>', 345, 53, '');
