INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(325, '2020~2030 建成中国的250吨级的深海空间站', '2020~2030 built 250 ton deep-sea space station China', '1535163754', '2018-08-25', '22:39:43', '2', '<p>目标是在2020年-2030年间，建成中国的250吨级的深海空间站，这一深海研究基地的将会是我们未来深海潜航员的门的家，在我们已经完成了35吨级别深海有人工作站和“蛟龙号”7000米级水下探测器的研制后，现在要建设的250吨级别深海空间站将会保障30人在水下1000米的深度工作至少60天。因为地球70%的海洋深度都是在1000米到2000米范围内，这样一种深海空间站已经足以满足我们现有要求。</p>', '<p> The target is in 2020 -2030 years, built 250 ton China deep space station, the deep-sea research base will be our future deep submerged member door in home, we have completed 35 tons of sea level one workstation and dragon developed 7000 meters underwater detector, 250 ton level deep space now want to build the station will protect the 30 person in the water depth of 1000 meters to work at least 60 days. Because 70% of the earth&#39;s ocean depth is 1000 meters to 2000 meters range, a deep-sea space station is sufficient to meet the requirements of our existing.</p>', 367, 92, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(326, '2020~2035 基本实现社会主义现代化', '2020~2035 the basic realization of socialist modernization', '1535163930', '2018-08-25', '22:39:03', '2', '<p>党的十九大明确作出了分两步走的战略部署:第一个阶段,从2020年到2035年,基本实现社会主义现代化</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> The party&#39;s nineteen clearly made a strategic plan is divided into two steps: the first stage, from 2020 to 2035, the basic realization of the socialist modernization</p><p><br/></p>', 332, 77, '');
INSERT INTO `page` VALUES(327, '2035~2050 把我国建成富强民主文明和谐美丽的社会主义现代化强国。', '2035~2050 turned China into a prosperous democratic and civilized and harmonious beauty of socialist modernization.', '1535164872', '2018-08-26', '08:26:12', '2', '<p>总目标是，到2050年，全面建成富强、民主、文明、和谐、绿色的社会主义现代化国家。其中包括六个方面的主要目标：</p><p>第一，   建成民富国强的社会主义现代化国家。</p><p>第二，   建成社会主义民主现代化国家。</p><p>第三，   建成更好文明的社会主义现代化国家。</p><p>第四，   建成更加和谐的社会主义现代化国家。</p><p>第五，   建成更加绿色的社会主义现代化国家。</p><p>第六，   建成对人类发展做出重大贡献的国家。</p><p>从核心指标来看，围绕六位一体总体布局从GDP为中心转向人的全面发展为中心。第一，从经济建设看，不再以追求高增长为目标，而是以经济持续健康稳定增长为目标，只规定经济增长底线。</p><p>第二，从社会建设看，要以改善民生为重点全面均衡推进社会建设，将人类发展指标作为核心指标之一。</p><p>第三，从生态建设看，要以民生环境为重点，重点解决人民群众关心的水、气、声、土壤等环境问题，重点解决农村的面源污染、饮用水安全、生态贫困等与人民利益密切相关的环境问题。</p><p>第四，从文化建设看，要以推进人民文化建设为重点，人民不但是文化消费主体，同时也是文化创作、参与文化的主体。</p><p>第五，从政治建设看，要以民生促进民主，以民主带动民生。</p><p>第六，从国防建设看，要确保国家安全，确保军队是一支听党指挥、能打胜仗、作风优良的人民军队。</p><p><br/></p>', '<p> The general goal is to 2050, fully completed powerful democratic civilized and harmonious modern socialist country green. Including the main target in six aspects:</p><p> First, built strong and modern socialist country.</p><p> Second, built socialist democratic modern country.</p><p> Third, built more civilized and modern socialist country.</p><p> Fourth, built more harmonious modern socialist country.</p><p> Fifth, built more green modern socialist country.</p><p> Sixth, built to make a significant contribution to human development countries.</p><p> From around the six core indicators, one overall layout from the GDP as the center to the comprehensive development of human centered. First, from the economic construction, not to pursue high growth as the goal, but to continue the healthy and stable economic growth as the goal, only the provisions of the bottom line of economic growth.</p><p> Second, from social construction, to focus on improving people&#39;s livelihood balanced to promote social development, human development index as the core index of.</p><p> Third, from the ecological construction, to the people&#39;s livelihood environment as the focus, focus on water, air, soil and other environmental issues of concern to the masses, the key to solve the environmental problems is closely related to the interests of the people of the rural non-point source pollution, drinking water safety, ecological poverty.</p><p> Fourth, from the cultural construction, to promote people&#39;s cultural construction as the focus, but not people&#39;s cultural consumption subject, the subject is also the cultural creation, cultural participation.</p><p> Fifth, from the political construction, to promote democracy to the people&#39;s livelihood, to democracy promoting people&#39;s livelihood.</p><p> Sixth, from the national defense construction, to ensure national security, ensure that the army is a command of the party, to win the war, people&#39;s army fine style.</p><p><br/></p>', 188, 77, '');
